quran[856]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Twa Seen Meem
  26,2,Lawa ngamavesi encwadi ecacile
  26,3,Siyazi ukuthi wena uphatheka kabi emphefumulweni ngenxa yokuthi abakholwa
  26,4,Uma sithanda singehlisela phezu kwabo uphawu oluvela ezulwini oluzokwenza ukuthi kugobe izintamo zabo ngokuzithoba
  26,5,Futhi angeke kufike kubona isikhumbuzo esisha esivela (kuMvelinqangi)onomusangaphandlekokubabayasifulathela
  26,6,Ngakho-ke ngempela bayenqaba (incwadi) ziyofika kubona izindaba zalokho ababenza inhlekisa ngako
  26,7,Ababheki yini emhlabeni ukuthi zingaki izinhlobo zezinto esenza ukuthi zimile kuwona na
  26,8,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo aliyibona abakholwayo
  26,9,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,10,Futhi (khumbula) ngenkathi iNkosi yakho ibiza uMose ukuthi akahambe aye kubantu abayizoni”
  26,11,"Abantu baFaro, ngakube abamesabi yini uMvelinqangi na"
  26,12,"Wathi, “Nkosi yami ngempela mina ngiyesaba ukuthi bazongiphika.”"
  26,13,Futhi isifuba sami siyacinana nolimi lwami alukhulumi kahle ngakho-ke thumela ukuthi kulandwe u-Aroni
  26,14,"Futhi mina nginecala kubona, ngakho-ke ngiyesaba ukuthi bazongibulala"
  26,15,"Wathi, “Qha hambani nobabili nezimpawu zethu ngempela thina sikanye nani, siyezwa”"
  26,16,Ngakho-ke hambani nobabili uma senifikile kuFaro nithi “thina siyizithunywa zeNkosi yemihlaba”
  26,17,Ngakho-ke bavumele abantwana bakwa-Israyeli bahambe kanye nathi
  26,18,"(UFaro) wathi (kuMose), “asizange yini sikukhulise phakathi kwethu njengomntwana futhi wahlala kanye nathi iminyaka eminingi yempilo yakho na?”"
  26,19,Futhi wenza isenzo sakho owasenza kulapho wena wawungomunye wabangabongi
  26,20,Wathi (uMose) “ngakwenza lokho ngenkathi mina ngangingomunye wabasephutheni”
  26,21,Ngakho-ke ngabaleka kunina ngenkathi nginesaba kepha iNkosi yami yangipha isehlulelo futhi yangenza ngaba ngomunye wezithunywa
  26,22,Futhi ngakube (iwona lowo) umusa ongikhumbuzisa wona ukuthi wagqilaza abantwana bakwa Israyeli na?”
  26,23,UFaro (Wabuza) wathi “futhi iyini iNkosi yemihlaba na?”
  26,24,(UMose waphendula) ngokuthi “iNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili uma kungukuthi nifuna ukuqiniseka”
  26,25,(UFaro) wathi “kulabo ababemzungezile “ngakube anikuzwa yini (lokho akushoyo) na?”
  26,26,"Wathi, “iNkosi yenu neNkosi yoyihlo basendulo”"
  26,27,"(UFaro) wathi, “ngempela isithunywa senu lesi esithunywe kunina siyahlanya”"
  26,28,"(UMose) wathi, “iNkosi yeMpumalanga neNtshonalanga kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili uma kungukuthi nina ninayo ingqondo”"
  26,29,"(UFaro) wathi, “uma ukhetha omunye uNkulunkulu esikhundleni sami ngempela ngizokwenza ukuthi ube ngomunye weziboshwa”"
  26,30,"UMose wathi, “yize noma ngingakulethela into esobala na?”"
  26,31,"(UFaro) wathi, “ilethe uma wena ungomunye wabaneqiniso”"
  26,32,Ngakho-ke (uMose) waphonsa phansi induku yakhe kwaba yilapho iphenduka inyoka egqamile
  26,33,Futhi wakhipha isandla sakhe kwaba yilapho simhlophe kwabasibonayo
  26,34,"(UFaro) wathi, ebaholini abamzungelezile ngempela lona ngumlumbi onolwazi olunzulu"
  26,35,Ufuna ukunigxosha ezweni lenu ngomlingo wakhe nicabanga ukuthi kwenziwe njani
  26,36,"Bathi, “mnike ithuba yena nomfowabo bese uthumela izigijimi emadolobheni”"
  26,37,Ukuze zikulethele bonke abalumbi abanolwazi olunzulu
  26,38,Ngakho-ke abalumbi baqoqelwa ndawonye ukuze kuqokwe isikhathi ngosuku olwaziwayo
  26,39,Futhi kwathiwa kubantu ngakube nina niyohlangana ndawonye na
  26,40,Ukuze sibalandele abelumbi uma bona bengabanqobayo
  26,41,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebefika abalumbi bathi kuFaro, “ngakube sizowuthola yini umvuzo uma thina singabanqobayo na?”"
  26,42,"UFarowathi,“yebofuthingempelaninanizobangabasondelayo (kumina)”"
  26,43,"UMose wathi kubona, “phonsani lokho enizokuphonsa”"
  26,44,"Ngakho-ke baziphonsa izintambo zabo kanye nezinduku zabo base bethi, “ngamandla kaFaro ngempela thina sizonqoba”"
  26,45,Ngakho-ke uMose wayiphonsa phansi induku yakhe kwaba yilapho – yona ikugwinya konke lokho okungamanga ababekuveza
  26,46,Ngakho-ke bawa abelumbi bajabalala
  26,47,"Bathi, “sikholiwe eNkosini yemihlaba”"
  26,48,In kosi kaMose no-Aroni”
  26,49,"(UFaro) wathi, “senikholiwe kuyona ngaphambi kokuba ngininike imvume ngempela yena (uMose) iyiNkosi yenu okuyiyona eyanifundisa umlingo ngakho-ke nizokwazi, ngempela ngizonquma izandla zenu kanye nezinyawo zenu ezinhlangothini ezehlukene futhi ngempela ngizoninqamuleza nonke”"
  26,50,"Bathi, “abukho ubungozi (asesabi lutho) ngempela thina siyophindela eNkosini yethu”"
  26,51,Siyethemba ukuthi iNkosi yethu izosithethelala ukona kwethu ngokuba singamakholwa okuqala”
  26,52,Futhi sembula kuMose ukuthi akahambe ebusuku kanye nezinceku zami ngempela nina nizolandelwa
  26,53,Ngakho-ke uFaro wathumela izigijimi emadolobheni
  26,54,Ngempela laba bayiqembu elincane
  26,55,Futhi ngempela bona bayasithukuthelisa
  26,56,Futhi ngempela thina saqaphelisa wonke umphakathi
  26,57,Ngakho-ke sabakhipha ezivandeni nasemithonjeni
  26,58,"Nasemicebweni\tnakuzona\tzonke\tizinhlobo\tzezindawo ezihloniphekile"
  26,59,Kanjalo sakunikeza lokho njengefa kubantwana bakwa- Israyeli
  26,60,Ngakho-ke babalandela ngasekuphumeni kwelanga
  26,61,"Kwathi lapho amaqembu amabili esebonana abalandeli baMose bathi, “ngempela sesificiwe”"
  26,62,"(UMose) wathi, “lutho! Ngempela iNkosi yami ikanye nami izongihola”"
  26,63,"Ngakho-ke sembula kuMose ukuthi, “shaya ulwande ngenduku yakho” lwaqhekeka phakathi ingxenye nengxenye yaphenduka yaba yigquma elikhulu elinjengentaba"
  26,64,Futhi sabasondeza abanye lapho
  26,65,Futhi samsindisa uMose kanye nababekanye naye bonke
  26,66,Sabe sesiyabaminzisa abanye
  26,67,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo alisibona abakholwayo
  26,68,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,69,Futhi bafundele indaba ka-Abrahamu
  26,70,"Khumbula\tngenkathi\tethi\tkuyise\tnakubantu\tbakhe, “nikhonzani na?”"
  26,71,"Bathi, “sikhonza izithombe, sizinikele kuzona.”"
  26,72,"(U-Abrahamu) wathi, “ngakube ziyanizwa yini uma nizibiza na?”"
  26,73,Noma ziwusizo kunina noma zinobungozi na
  26,74,"Bathi, “Qhabo! Safica obaba bethu benzenjalo (bezikhonza izithixo).”"
  26,75,"U-Abrahamu wathi, “Ngakube nikubonile yini lokho nina enanikukhonza”"
  26,76,Nina kanye naboyihlo basendulo na
  26,77,Ngakho-ke ngempela bona bayizitha kumina ngaphandle kweNkosi yemihlaba
  26,78,"Okuyiyona eyangidalayo, yona iyangihola"
  26,79,Futhi iyona engipha ukudla nengiphuzisayo
  26,80,Futhi uma ngigula yona iyangelapha
  26,81,Futhi iyona eyokwenza ukuthi ngife bese ingipha ukuphila
  26,82,Futhi iyona engethemba ukuthi iyongithethelela amaphutha ami ngosuku lwenkokhelo
  26,83,Nkosi yami ngiphe ukwehlulela (ukuhola okuyiqiniso) futhi ungihlanganise nabalungileyo
  26,84,Futhi ngiphe udumo ezizukulwaneni ezilandelayo
  26,85,"Futhi\tngenze\tngibe\tngomunye\twezindlalifa\tzesivande senjabulo"
  26,86,"Futhi\tthethelela\tubaba\tngempela\tyena\tungomunye wabadukileyo"
  26,87,Futhi ungangiphathi kabi ngosuku lapho beyobe bevuswa
  26,88,Ngosuku lapho umnotho nezingane kungeke kusize ngalutho
  26,89,"Ngaphandle\tkwalowo\toyoza\tkuMvelinqangi\tnenhliziyo emsulwa"
  26,90,Futhi izulu liyosondezelwa abesaba uMvelinqangi
  26,91,Futhi isihogo siyovezelwa obala labo abaphambukileyo
  26,92,"Futhi kuyothiwa kubona, “kuphi lokho enanikukhonza na?”"
  26,93,Esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi na? Ngakube kuyanisiza noma kuyazisiza na
  26,94,Ngakho-ke bayophonswa kusona (isihogo) bona kanye nabaphambukileyo
  26,95,Kanye namabutho kasathane wonke
  26,96,Lapho phakathi bona bayoxabana bathi
  26,97,Sifunga ngoMvelinqangi! Ngempela sasisekudukeni okucacile
  26,98,Ngenkathi sinilinganisa neNkosi yemihlaba
  26,99,Futhi akekho owasidukisa ngaphandle kwezoni
  26,100,Ngakho-ke asinaye ongomunye wabancengeli
  26,101,Noma umngane omnene
  26,102,Ngakho-ke ukube besingaphindela (emhlabeni) besizokuba ngabanye babakholwayo
  26,103,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo alikholwa
  26,104,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,105,Abantu baNowa baziphika izithunywa
  26,106,"Khumbula ngenkathi umfowabo uNowa ethi kubona, “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi?”"
  26,107,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,108,Ngakho-ke mesabeni uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,109,"Futhi angiwuceli kunina umvuzo ngako, umvuzo wami angiwutholi (komunye umuntu) ngaphandle kokuwucela eNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,110,Ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,111,"Bathi, “singakholelwa yini kuwena kulapho ulandelwa ngabantu abasezingeni eliphansi kakhulu na?”"
  26,112,Wathi. “Futhi yiluphi ulwazi enginalo ngalokho ababekwenza na?”
  26,113,Ukwahlulelwa kwabo kuseNkosini yami ukube nje benazi
  26,114,Futhi angeke ngiwagxoshe amakholwa
  26,115,Mina angiyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngumxwayisi ocacile
  26,116,"Bathi, “uma ungaphezi Oh Nowa! Ngempela uzokuba ngomunye walabo abakhandwa ngamatshe”"
  26,117,"(UNowa) wathi, “Nkosi yami ngempela abantu bami bangiphika.”"
  26,118,Ngakho-ke yehlulela phakathi kwami nabo futhi ungisindise kanye nanoma ngabe ngobani abakanye nami abangamakholwa
  26,119,"Ngakho-ke\tsamsindisa\tkanye\tnalabo\tabakanye\tnaye emkhunjini othweleyo"
  26,120,Sabe sesibaminzisa abanye emva kwalokho
  26,121,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo lalingesiwona amakholwa
  26,122,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,123,Abantu base A’d baziphika izithunywa
  26,124,"Khumbula\tngenkathi\tumfowabo\tuHud\tethi\tkubona “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi?”"
  26,125,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,126,Ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphile
  26,127,"Futhi angiwufuni umvuzo kunina ngako, umvuzo wami angiwutholi komunye umuntu ngaphandle kokuwuthola eNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,128,Ngakube nenza uphawu phezu kwazo zonke izindawo eziphakeme? Niyazithokozisa
  26,129,Futhi nizithathele izindlu ezinkulu ezidephile ezinohlonze ukuze nihlale kuzona ingunaphakade
  26,130,"Futhi uma nishaya, nishaya ngobudlova"
  26,131,Ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,132,Futhi mesabeni lowo owanilekelela ngalokho enikwaziyo
  26,133,Wanilekelela ngezinkomo nangezingane
  26,134,Nangezivande nangemithombo
  26,135,Ngempela mina ngiyanesabela isijeziso sosuku olukhulu
  26,136,"Bathi,\t“kuyefana\tkuthina\tnoma\tuyashumayela\tnoma awusiyena omunye wabashumayelayo”"
  26,137,"Lokhu\takuyilutho\tngaphandle\tkokuba\tkube\tyinkolo yasendulo"
  26,138,Futhi thina angeke sijeziswe
  26,139,"Ngakho-ke bamphika sabe sesibabhubhisa, ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo lalingesiwona amakholwa"
  26,140,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,141,Abantu baThamud baziphika izithunywa
  26,142,Khumbula ngenkathi umfowabo uSwalih ethi kubona “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi.”
  26,143,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,144,Ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,145,"Futhi angiwufuni kunina umvuzo ngako, umvuzo wami awukho komunye umuntu ngaphandle kokuba useNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,146,Ngakube nizoyekwa niphephile kulokhu enikukona lapha
  26,147,Ezivandeni nasemithonjeni
  26,148,Nasemasimini nasezihlahleni zesundu isixha sazo sithambile
  26,149,Futhi nimba izintaba ngobiciko ukuze nakhe izindlu
  26,150,Ngakho-ke mesabeni uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,151,Futhi ningayihloniphi impoqo yezaphulamthetho
  26,152,"Labo abenza ukona ezweni, abangalungisi"
  26,153,"Bathi, “kuphela wena ungomunye wabalunjiwe”"
  26,154,Awuyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngumuntu onjengathi ngakho-ke makunjalo veza uphawu uma kungukuthi wena ungomunye wabaqinisile
  26,155,"Wathi, “leli yikameli lensikazi linelungelo lokuphuza, nani ninelungelo lokuphuza ngosuku olwaziwayo”"
  26,156,Futhi ningalithinti ngobubi hleze nithathwe yisijeziso sosuku olukhulu
  26,157,Kepha balibulala (ikameli) base bephenduka abazisolayo
  26,158,"Ngakho-ke\tbathathwa\tyisijeziso,\tngempela\tkulokho kunesifundo futhi iningi labo lalingeyibona abakholwayo"
  26,159,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,160,Abantu baLothi baziphika izithunywa
  26,161,"Khumbula\tngenkathi\tumfowabo\tuLothi\tethi\tkubona “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi?”"
  26,162,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,163,Ngakho-ke mesabeni uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,164,"Futhi angiwufuni kunina umvuzo ngako, umvuzo wami awukho komunye umuntu ngaphandle kokuthi useNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,165,Ngakube phakathi kwezidalwa (nikhetha) ukuya kwabesilisa na
  26,166,"Futhi niyeka labo iNkosi yenu eyanidalela bona ukuba babe ngamakhosikazi enu, Qhabo! Nina ningabantu abephula umthetho"
  26,167,"Bathi, “Oh Lothi! uma ungaphezi ngempela uzokuba ngomunye wabagxoshiwe”"
  26,168,"Wathi, “Ngempela mina lesisenzo senu angisithandi”"
  26,169,Nkosi yami ngisindise kanye nomndeni wami kulokhu abakwenzayo
  26,170,Ngakho-ke samsindisa kanye nomndeni wakhe wonke
  26,171,Ngaphandle konkosikazi omdala phakathi kwalabo ababesalele ngemumva
  26,172,Sabe sesibabhubhisa abanye
  26,173,"Futhi sayinethisa imvula phezu kwabo, imvula eyayiyimbi kulabo ababexwayisiwe"
  26,174,Ngempelakulokhukunesifundofuthiiningilabolalingesiwona amakholwa
  26,175,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,176,Izihlali zase-Aykah zaziziphika izithunywa
  26,177,Khumbula ngenkathi uShuaib ethi kuzona “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi?”
  26,178,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,179,Ngakho-ke mesabeni uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,180,"Futhi angiwufuni kunina umvuzo ngako, umvuzo wami angiwutholi komunye umuntu ngaphandle kokuwuthola eNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,181,Nikezani isilinganiso esigcwele futhi ningabi ngabanye balabo abayimbangela yokulahleka
  26,182,Futhi linganisani ngesikalo esiyiqiniso nesiqondile
  26,183,Futhi ningayidli impahla yabantu ngamacebo ngokuyehlisa futhi ningenzi ukona emhlabeni
  26,184,"Futhi\tmesabeni\tlowo\towanidala\tkanye\tnezizukulwane zasendulo"
  26,185,"Bathi, “kuphela wena ungomunye walabo abalunjiwe”"
  26,186,Futhi wena awuyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngumuntu ofananathi futhi sicabanga ukuthi ungomunye wabaqamba amanga
  26,187,Ngakho-ke makunjalo yehlisela phezu kwethu ingxenye yezulu uma kungukuthi ungomunye wabaqinisileyo
  26,188,"Wathi, “iNkosi yami eyazi kangcono ngaloko enikwenzayo”"
  26,189,"Kepha bamphika, ngakho-ke yisijeziso sosuku lwethunzi, ngempela leso kwakuyisijeziso sosuku olukhulu"
  26,190,"Ngempela\tkulokho\tkunesifundo\tfuthi\tiningi\tlabo lalingeyiwona amakholwa"
  26,191,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,192,Futhi ngempela lesi yisambulo seNkosi yemihlaba
  26,193,"Esehliselwe\tphansi\tngumoya\tongcwele\t(uGabriyeli) owethembekile"
  26,194,Enhliziyweni yakho ukuze ube ngomunye wabaxwayisi
  26,195,Ngolimi lwesi-Arabhu olucacile
  26,196,Futhi ngempela yona (iQur’an) kwakubikezelwe ngayo emibhalweni yasemandulo
  26,197,Akusilona yini uphawu kubona ukuthi izifundiswa zabantwana bakwa-Israyeli ziyayazi (iQur’an) na
  26,198,Ngisho noma ngabe sasiyembule kwabanye bakwelinye izwe
  26,199,Bese eyabafundela babengeke babe ngabakholelwa kuyona
  26,200,Kanjalo sayenza ukuthi ingene igxile ezinhliziyweni zezoni
  26,201,Abakholelwa kuyona kuze kube yilapho bebona khona isijeziso esibuhlungu
  26,202,Ngakho-ke siyobafikela masinyane kulapho bona benganakile
  26,203,"Bayothi, “ngakube thina sizonikwa yini na ithuba?”"
  26,204,Ngakube basafuna yini ukusisheshisa isijeziso sethu na
  26,205,"Ngakube\tubonile\tyini\tukuthi\tsabathokozisa\timinyaka eminingi na"
  26,206,Kwabe sekufika kubona lokho ababethenjiswe kona na
  26,207,Akuzange kubasize lokho ababezijabulisa ngako
  26,208,Futhi alikho idolobha esalibhubhisa elalingenabo abexwayisi balo
  26,209,"Ngendlela\teyisikhumbuzo,\tfuthi\tasikaze\tsenze okungenabulungiswa"
  26,210,Futhi akuyibona osathane abayiletha phansi(iQuran)
  26,211,Futhi akubafanele (osathane ukwenza lokho) futhi abanawo amandla
  26,212,Ngempela bona baqhelelanisiwe nokuzwa
  26,213,"Ngakho-ke\tungambizi\tuMvelinqangi\tkanye\tnomunye uNkulunkulu ngokuba uzoba ngomunye wabajeziswayo"
  26,214,Futhi zixwayise izihlobo zakho ezisondele kakhulu
  26,215,Futhi yiba mnene kunoma ngabe ngubani okulandelayo kwabakholwayo
  26,216,"Kepha uma bengakuhloniphi ngakho-ke ithi, “ngempela mina ngimsulwa kulokho enikwenzayo”"
  26,217,Futhi thembela kophakeme ngamandla onesihawu
  26,218,Lowo okubonayo uma usukuma emthandazweni
  26,219,Nokuhamba phakathi kwalabo abaguqile bezithobile
  26,220,"Ngempela yena ungozwayo, owaziyo"
  26,221,Ngakube nginitshelile yini ukuthi osathane behlela phezu kukabani na
  26,222,Behlela phezu kwabona bonke abaqamba amanga abanezono
  26,223,Bayamlalela (usathane) futhi iningi labo lingabaqambimanga
  26,224,"Kanye nezimbongi, abaphambukayo bayazilandela"
  26,225,Awuboni yini ukuthi bona bayazulazula kuzona zonke izigodi
  26,226,Nokuthi bona basho lokho abangakwenzi
  26,227,Ngaphandle kwalabo abakholwayo abenza izenzo ezilungileyo futhi abakhumbula uMvelinqangi kaningi futhi abavikelayo emva kokuba benziwe okungenabulungiswa futhi bayokwazi labo abenza okungenabo ubulungiswa ukuthi iyiphi indawo yokuphenduka abayophendukela kuyona
  27,1,"TA SEEN. Lawa ngamavesi eQur’an, futhi incwadi eyenza kucace"
  27,2,Eholayo nenikeza abakholwayo izindaba ezimnandi
  27,3,Labo abenza umthandazo futhi abakhokha ingxenye yengcebo yabo kwabampofu kulapho bona beqinisekile ngempilo ezayo
  27,4,Ngempela labo abangakholelwa empilweni ezayo sibenzele ukuthi imisebenzi yabo ibukeke imihle kubona ukuze bazulazule bephuphutheka
  27,5,Labo-ke bayilabo okwabo okuyisijeziso esibi futhi bona empilweni ezayo bayoba ngabalahlekelwe kakhulu ukwedlula bonke
  27,6,Futhi ngempela wena wenziwe ukuthi wemukela iQur’an konobuhlakani owaziyo
  27,7,"Khumbula ngenkathi uMose ethi emndenini wakhe, “ngempela mina ngibona umlilo ngizonilethela izindaba ezivela kuwona noma nginilethele amalahle ashisayo ukuze nizifudumeze”"
  27,8,Ngenkathi efika kuwona (umlilo) wamenyezwa kwathiwa “ubusisiwe noma ngabe ngubani osemlilweni nanoma ngabe ngubani owuzungelezile” futhi udumo malube kuMvelinqangi iNkosi yemihlaba
  27,9,Oh Mose! Ngempela mina nginguMvelinqangi ophakeme ngamandla onobuhlakani
  27,10,"Futhi phonsa phansi induku yakho, ngakho-ke kwathi lapho eyibona inyakaza sengathi inyoka waphenduka wabaleka wangabheki\temumva,\t“Oh\tMose!\tUngesabi\tngempela azingesabi izithunywa ezikanye nami”"
  27,11,"Ngaphandle kwalowo owenza okungenabulungiswa bese eshintsha okuhle emva kokubi, ngakho-ke ngempela mina ngingothethelelayo onesihawu"
  27,12,"Futhi faka isandla sakho ephaketheni lakho sizophuma simhlophe singenabubi (lezi ngezinye) zezimpawu eziyisishiyagalolunye oyoziyisa kuFaro nabantu bakhe, ngempela bona bangabantu abangalungile abayizoni"
  27,13,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sezifika kubona izimpawu zethu ezibonakalayo bathi, “lona ngumlingo ocacile”"
  27,14,"Futhi baziphika (lezo zimpawu) ngokungemthetho nangokuqhosha kulapho imiphefumulo yabo yenelisekile, ngakho-ke bheka ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho sezoni"
  27,15,"Futhi ngempela samnikeza ulwazi uDavide noSolomoni bobabili base bathi, “Udumo malube kuMvelinqangi okunguyena owasikhetha ngaphezu kwezinceku zakhe eziningi ezingamakholwa”"
  27,16,"USolomoni wadla ifa (ubuphrofethi) kuDavide wayesethi, “Oh Bantu! Sifundiswe ulimi lwezinyoni futhi siphiwe kuzona zonke izinto, ngempela lobu ngububele obugqamile”"
  27,17,Futhi kwaqoqelwa ndawonye kuSolomoni amabutho akhe angamaJinn nabantu kanye nezinyoni wonke ayemiswe ngendlela yempi (belungele ukuhamba)
  27,18,"Kwaze kwaba yilapho befinyelela khona esigodini sezintuthwane enye yezintuthwane yathi, “Oh Zintuthwane! ngenani ezindlini zenu hleze uSolomoni namabutho akhe anifihlize kulapho bona bengaboni”"
  27,19,"Ngakho-ke (uSolomoni) wamomotheka ehleka inkulumo yayo wayesethi, “Nkosi yami ngenze ukuthi ngibonge ububele bakho owangenzela bona kanye nabazali bami futhi ngenze umsebenzi olungileyo owuthokozelayo futhi ngingenise ngomusa wakho phakathi kwezinceku zakho ezilungileyo”"
  27,20,"Futhi wazihlola izinyoni wayesethi, “kwenziwa yini ukuthi ngingamboni uHud Hud noma ungomunye walabo abangekho na?”"
  27,21,Ngempela ngizomjezisa ngesijeziso esinzima noma ngempela ngimbulale ngaphandle uma engitshela isizathu esicacile
  27,22,"Akazange ahlale isikhathi eside wayesethi, “ngithole lokho ongazange ukuthole futhi ngikulethele izindaba eziyiqiniso ezivela kuSaba”"
  27,23,Ngempela mina ngifice owesifazane ebabusa futhi uphiwe kuzona zonke izinto futhi unesihlalo sobukhosi esikhulu
  27,24,Ngimfumane ekanye nabantu bakhe bekhonza ilanga esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi futhi uSathane wabenzela yabukeka imihle imisebenzi yabo kubona wayesebavimbela endleleni (eqondile) ngakho-ke bona abaholekanga
  27,25,Abamkhonzi uMvelinqangi okunguyena oveza okufihlekile emazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi owazi konke lokho enikufihlayo nakho konke lokho enikuvezayo
  27,26,UMvelinqangi akekho omunye uMvelinqangi ngaphandle kwakhe uyiNkosi yesihlalo sobukhosi esikhulu
  27,27,"Wathi, “sizobona ukuthi ukhuluma iqiniso noma ungomunye walabo abaqamba amanga”"
  27,28,Hamba nalencwadi yami bese uyijikijela kubona bese uyabafulathela bese uyabheka ukuthi yini abayibuyisayo
  27,29,"Owesifazane wathi, “Oh Baphathi! Ngempela kujikijelwe kumina incwadi engcwele”"
  27,30,Ngempela yona ivela kuSolomoni futhi ngempela yona ingegama likaMvelinqangi onomusa onesihawu
  27,31,Ningaziphakamisi kumina futhi yizani kumina ngokuzinikela
  27,32,"Wathi owesifazane, “Oh Baphathi! ngelulekeni odabeni lwami, angeke ngikhiphe isinqumo odabeni kuze kube yilapho nikhona kanye nami.”"
  27,33,"Bathi, “thina singabanamandla amakhulu futhi singabanempi enkulu, impoqo ingeyakho, ngakho-ke cabanga ukuthi uzophoqa ukuba kwenziweni”"
  27,34,"Yathi indlovukazi, “ngempela amakhosi uma engena edolobheni enza ukona kulona bese enza abantu balo abahloniphekile ukuthi babesezingeni eliphansi futhi enza kanjalo”"
  27,35,Futhi ngempela mina ngizothumela kubona isipho bese ngibheka ukuthi yini izithunywa ezizobuya nayo
  27,36,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sezifika (izithunywa) kuSolomoni nesipho wathi “ngakube ningelekelela ngengcebo na? Lokho uMvelinqangi angipha kona kungcono kunalokho anipha kona kepha nina nithokozile ngesipho senu”
  27,37,"Phindelani kubona ngempela thina sizoza kubona namabutho empi abangeke bakwazi ukuwavimba futhi ngempela sizobakhipha lapho ngechilo, futhi bayobe bethotshisiwe”"
  27,38,"Wathi, “Oh Baphathi! Ngubani phakathi kwenu ozongilethela isihlalo sobukhosi sakhe owesifazane ngaphambi kokuba bafike kumina bezinikele ngokuzithoba”"
  27,39,"Elinye lamaJinn lathi, “Mina ngizosiletha kuwena ngaphambi kokuba usukume endaweni yakho futhi ngempela mina nginamandla ngethembekile”"
  27,40,"Lowo onolwazi lencwadi wathi, “ngizosiletha kuwena ngaphambi kokuphazima kweso lakho” Mina ngizosiletha kuwena ngaphambi kokuphazima kweso lakho” ngakho- ke kwathi lapho esibona sibekwe eduzane naye wathi “lokhu kungomusa weNkosi yami ukuze ingivivinye ukuthi ngiyabonga noma angibongi futhi noma ngabe ngubani obongayo kuphela ubongela umphefumulo wakhe f u t h i noma ngabe ngubani ongabongi ngakho-ke ngempela iNkosi yami ayidingi lutho ihloniphekile”"
  27,41,"Wathi, “sisithezeleni owesifazane isihlalo sakhe sobukhosi (ukuze angasiboni ukuthi yisona noma akusiyona) ukuze sibone ukuthi owesifazane ungoholiweyo noma ungomunye walabo abangaholiwe”"
  27,42,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho esefika owesifazane kwathiwa “ngakube sinjena yini na isihlalo sakho sobukhosi?” Owesifazane wathi,“ungathi yisona” (uSolomoni wathi) “futhi sinikeziwe ulwazi ngaphambilini kwakhe owesifazane futhi sasizinikele ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi”"
  27,43,Futhi kwamvimba lokho ayekukhonza esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi ngempela yena owesifazane wayengomunye walabobantu abangakholwa
  27,44,"Kwathiwa kuyena owesifazane, “ngena endlini yobukhosi edephile” kwathi lapho owesifazane eseyibona wacabanga ukuthi indawo yayo yaphansi yakhiwe ngamanzi (noma kunedamu lamanzi ngaphansi kwendlu enkulu yobukhosi waphakamisa izingubo zakhe) kwavela imilenze yakhe (uSolomoni) wathi “ngempela yindlu yobukhosi eyenziwe ngengilazi” owesifazane wathi “Nkosi yami ngempela mina ngenze okungalungile emphefumulweni wami futhi ngiyazinikela kanye noSolomoni kuMvelinqangi iNkosi yemihlaba”"
  27,45,Futhi ngempela sathumela kuThamud umfowabo uSalih ukuthi khonzani uMvelinqangi kulapho bona bengamaqembu amabili angaboni ngasolinye
  27,46,"Wathi, “Oh Bantu bami! kungani nijaha ebubini ngaphambi kokuhle na? Aniyiceli ngani intethelelo kaMvelinqangi ukuze mhlawumbe ninikwe umusa na?”"
  27,47,"Bathi, “sihlahla umhlola kuwena kanye nalabo abakanye nawe” wathi, “umhlola wenu ukuMvelinqangi kepha nina ningabantu abavivinywayo”"
  27,48,Futhi edolobheni kwakukhona abantu abayisishiyagalolunye ababenza ukona ezweni futhi bangalungisi
  27,49,"Bathi, “makafunge omunye komunye ngoMvelinqangi ukuthi ngempela sizomhlasela ebusuku kanye nomndeni wakhe bese ngempela sithi esihlotsheni sakhe “asikubonanga okubhubhise abantu bakhe futhi ngempela thina sikhuluma iqiniso”"
  27,50,Futhi benza icebo nathi senza icebo kulapho bona bengaboni
  27,51,"Ngakho-ke bheka ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho secebo labo, ngempela sababhubhisa kanye nabantu babo ndawonye"
  27,52,Ngakho-ke lezozindlu zabo zadilika ngenxa yokuthi babonile ngempela kulokho kunophawu (nesifundo) kubantu abaziyo
  27,53,Futhi sabasindisa labo ababekholwa futhi ababemesaba uMvelinqangi
  27,54,"Kanye noLothi khumbula ngenkathi ethi kubantu bakhe, “ngakube nenza izenzo ezingalungile kulapho nina nibona na?”"
  27,55,Ngakube ngempela nina nikhanukela amadoda esikhundleni sabesifazane na? Qhabo! Nina ningabantu abangenalo ulwazi
  27,56,Ayibanga yilutho impendulo yabantu bakhe ngaphandle kokuthi bathi “asiwukhipheni umndeni kaLothi edolobheni lenu ngempela bona bayibantu abahlanzekile abamsulwa”
  27,57,Ngakho-ke samsindisa kanye nomdeni wakhe ngaphandle konkosikazi wakhe samenza ukuba abe ngomunye wabasalela ngemumva
  27,58,Futhi sayinethisa phezu kwabo imvula kangangoba kwakuyimvula embi yalabo ababexwayisiwe
  27,59,"Ithi, “udumo lungolukaMvelinqangi futhi ukuthula makube ezincekwini zakhe lezo azikhetha, ngakuba uMvelinqangi ungcono noma yilokho abamenzela ngakho abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni na?”"
  27,60,"Ubani owadala amazulu nomhlaba futhi wanehlisela phansi amanzi avela esibhakabhakeni sabe sesikhulisa ngayo izivande ezinhle ezijabulile? Angeke nibe nawo amandla okukhulisa izihlahla zawo, ngakube ukhona yini unkulunkulu okanye noMvelinqangi na? Kepha bona bangabantu abenza abalingani"
  27,61,"Akusiyena yini owenza umhlaba waba yindawo yokuhlala wayesebeka imifula kuwona futhi wabeka izintaba kuwona futhi wabeka isehlukaniso phakathi kwezilwandle ezimbili, ngakube ukhona yini unkulunkulu okanye noMvelinqangi na? Kepha iningi labo alazi"
  27,62,Ubani ophendula lowo ophelelwe yithemba uma emmemeza futhi asuse okubi bese enenza nibe yisizukulwane esilandelayo emhlabeni na? Ngakube ukhona yini unkululnkulu okanye noMvelinqangi na? Kuncane enikukhumbulayo
  27,63,Ubani oniholayo ebumnyameni bezwe nolwandle futhi othumela imimoya njengezindaba ezimnandi ngaphambi komusa wakhe na? Uphakeme uMvelinqangi ngaphezu kwalokho abamenzela ngako abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni
  27,64,Ubani osungula indalo bese eyiphinda futhi anabele ngokuvela ezulwini nasemhlabeni ngakube ukhona yini unkulunkulu okanye noMvelinqangi na? Ithi “lethani ubufakazi benu uma kungukuthi nina nineqiniso”
  27,65,"Ithi, “akekho ngisho noyedwa osemazulwini nasemhlabeni owazi okungabonwayo ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi futhi abazi ukuthi bayovuswa nini kwabafileyo”"
  27,66,Qhabo! abanalo ulwazi ngempilo ezayo qhabo bona basekungabazeni ngayo Kepha bona bayizimpumputhe ngayo
  27,67,Futhi labo abangakholwanga bathi ngakube uma sesiwuthuli kanye nobaba bethu ngempela siyovezwa (sibe yizidalwa ezintsha yini na)
  27,68,Ngempela sathenjiswa lokhu thina kanye nabobaba bethu ngaphambilini lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle kokuthi kuyizinganekwane zabantu basendulo
  27,69,Ithi hambani ezweni bese niyabona ukuthi sabayini isiphetho sezoni
  27,70,Futhi ungaphatheki kabi ngabo futhi ungabi lusizi ngalokho abenza ngako icebo
  27,71,"Futhi bathi, “siyogcwaliseka nini lesisithembiso uma kungukuthi nina nineqeniso na?”"
  27,72,"Ithi, “mhlawumbe kuseduzane emumva kwenu okunye kwalokho enifuna ukuba kusheshe”"
  27,73,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho ingumnikazi womusa ebantwini kepha iningi labo alibongi
  27,74,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho iyakwazi lokho izifuba zabo ezikufihlayo kanye nalokho ezikuvezayo
  27,75,Futhi akukho lutho olufihlekile ezulwini nasemhlabeni ngaphandle kokuthi kusencwadini ecacile
  27,76,Ngempela leQur’an izekela abantwana bakwa-Israyeli labo abaningi babo abaphikisanayo ngako
  27,77,Futhi ngempela ukuholwa nomusa kungokwabakholwayo
  27,78,Ngempela iNkosi yakho iyokwehlulela phakathi kwabo ngesehlulelo sayo futhi yona iphakeme ngamandla inolwazi
  27,79,Ngakho-ke yethembela kuMvelinqangi ngempela wena useqinisweni eligqamile
  27,80,Ngempela wena angeke wenze abafile ukuthi bezwe futhi angeke wenze izithuli ukuba zizwe ukumenyezwa uma sezifulathele zibaleka
  27,81,"Futhi wena angeke uzihole izimpumputhe ekudukeni kwazo, ungenza ukuthi bezwe labo abakholelwa emavesini ethu ngakho-ke labo bangabazinikele ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi"
  27,82,Futhi uma behlelwa yizwi sizobavezela isidalwa esinyakazayo esiphuma emhlabeni ukuthi sikhulume nabo ngoba abantu abazange baqiniseke ngamavesi ethu
  27,83,Futhi ngosuku lapho siyoqoqa kuleso nalesosizwe iqembu phakathi kwalabo ababephika amavesi ethu bese beyiswa (endaweni yokwahlulelwa)
  27,84,"Kuzekuthi uma befika athi ngakube naniwaphika yini amavesi ami kulapho naningenalo ulwazi ngawo, kwakuyini lena enayiyenza na"
  27,85,Futhi izwi liyogcwaliseka kubona ngenxa yokuthi bebenza okungenabo ubulungiswa ngakho-ke bona angeke bakhulume
  27,86,Ababoni yini ukuthi sabenza ubusuku ukuthi baphumule kubona nemini ukuze ibanike ukukhanya na? ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kubantu abakholwayo
  27,87,"Futhi ngosuku lapho kuyobe kushawa ngalo icilongo, noma ngabe ngubani osemazulwini noma ngabe ngubani osemhlabeni uyokwesaba ngaphandle kwalabo ngokuthanda kukaMvelinqangi, futhi bonke bayoza kuyena bezithobile"
  27,88,"Futhi uyobona izintaba ucabange ukuthi zisimeme kulapho zona ziyobe zidlula njengokudlula kwamafu, okwenziwe nguMvelinqangi okunguyena owenzisisa kahle zonke izinto, ngempela yena unolwazi olunzulu ngalokho enikwenzayo"
  27,89,Noma ngabe ngubani ofike nokuhle ngakho-ke okwakhe okungcono kunako futhi bona bayophepha ekwesabeni kwangalolosuku
  27,90,"Futhi noma ngabe ngubani oyofika nokubi buyophonswa emlilweni ubuso babo, ngakube niyonikezwa omunye umvuzo ngaphandle kwalokho enanikwenza na"
  27,91,"Kuphela ngiphoqiwe ukuba ngikhonze iNkosi yalelidolobha (Makkag) elenze labangcwele futhi kungokwakhe, futhi ngiphoqiwe ukuthi ngibe ngomunye wabazinikele ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi"
  27,92,"Futhi (ngiphoqiwe) ukuba ngifunde iQur’an ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani oholiwe kuphela uholelwe umphefumulo wakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani odukayo ngakho-ke ithi, “kuphela mina ngingomunye wabaxwayisi”"
  27,93,"Futhi ithi, “Udumo lungolukaMvelinqangi uzonikhombisa amavesi akhe ukuze niwazi futhi akusikona ukuthi iNkosi yakho ayikunakile lokho enikwenzayo”"
  28,1,Twa Seen Meem
  28,2,Lawa ngamavesi encwadi ecacile
  28,3,"Siwafundela wena ngeqinso ezindabeni zikaMose kanye noFaro, ebantwini abakholwayo"
  28,4,"Ngempela uFaro waziphakamisa emhlabeni wenza abantu bawo amaqembu ecindezela iqembu (labantwana baka-Israel) phakathi kwabo ebulala amadodana abo eshiya abesifazane babo bephila, ngempela yena wayengomunye wabacindezeli"
  28,5,"Futhi sasifuna ukubeka umusa phezu kwalabo ababenziwe baba buthakathaka emhlabeni, futhi sibenze babengabaholi futhi sibenze izindlalifa"
  28,6,"Futhi sibazinzise emhlabeni futhi sikhombize ufaro, Haman kanye namabuthoabo bobabili avela phakathi kwabo lokho abakwesabayo"
  28,7,"Futhi sakwembula kunina kaMose ukuthi amncelise uma unokwesaba ngaye ngakho-ke mphonse emfuleni, ungesabi futhi ungaphatheki kabi ngempela thina sizomphindise la kuwena futhi sizomenza omunye wezithunywa"
  28,8,"Ngakho-ke abantu baFaro bamthatha ukuze abeyisitha nosizi kubona, ngempela uFaro noHaman kanye namabutho abo bobabili babeyizoni"
  28,9,"Futhi unkosikazi kaFaro wathi, “ungumduduzi wehlo lami nehlo lakho ungambulali angase abewusizo kuthina noma simthathe njengendodana” lapho bengazi"
  28,10,"Futhi inhliziyo kanina kaMose yaba igobongo, wacishe wamveza ukube sasingayiqinisanga inhliziyo yakhe ukuze ahlale engomunye wabakholwayo"
  28,11,Futhi owesifazane (unina ka-Mose) wathi kudadewabo wesilisa “mlandele owesilisa” owesifazane (udade wabo) wayesembheka owesilisa ebuqamama kulapho bona bengaboni
  28,12,"Futhi ngaphambilini samuqabela ukuthi angancela kwabanye abancelisi bese udade wabo wayesithi, “nginganikhombisa yini abantu bomndeni abazonikhulisela yena futhi abazomeluleka na?”"
  28,13,Ngakho-ke samphindisela kunina ukuze amehlo akhe aduduzeke futhi angabi lusizi nokuthi azi ukuthi isethembiso sika Mvelinqangi siyiqiniso kepha iningi labo alazi
  28,14,"Futhi kwathi lapho esekhulile ngokuphelele samupha ubuhlakani nolwazi, sibapha kanjalo umvuzo abenza okuhle"
  28,15,"Futhi (uMose) wangena edolobheni ngenkathi abantu balo benganakile wafica khona amadoda amaibili elwa omunye engoweqembu lakhe futhi omunye (engoweqembu) lezitha zakhe, ngakho-ke lowo ongoweqembu lakhe wacela usizo kuyena ukuze abhekane nesitha sakhe, ngakho-ke uMose wamshaya ngesibhakela wambulala wathi “lokhu kungomunye womsebenzi kasathane, ngempela yena uyisitha esicacile esidukisayo"
  28,16,"Wathi, “Nkosi yami ngempela mina ngiwonile umphefumulo wami ngakho-ke ngithethelele” yamthethelela ngempela yona iyathethelela inesihawu"
  28,17,"Wathi, “Nkosi yami, ngenxa yobubele ongenzele bona ngakho-ke angisoze ngaba ngumsizi wezoni”"
  28,18,"Ngakho-ke waphenduka owesabayo edolobheni ebheka emaceleni, kulapho lowo owayecele kuyena usizo ngayizolo ecela usizo kuyena uMose wathi kuyena “ngempela wena uhlale unochuku olugqamile”"
  28,19,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho efuna ukumbamba lowo oyisitha sabo bobabili wathi, “Oh Mose! Ngakube ufuna ukungibulala njengoba ubulale umuntu izolo na? awufuni lutho ngaphandle kokuba yisidlova ezweni futhi awufuni ukuba ngomunye wabalungileyo”"
  28,20,"Futhi kweza umuntu egijima eqhamuka endaweni eqhelelene kakhulu nedolobha wathi, “Oh Mose! Ngempela abaholi babopha uzungu ngawe ukuthi bakubulale ngakho-ke hamba ngempela mina ngingomunye wabeluleki"
  28,21,"Ngakho-kewemukakulona(idolobha) esaba, ejeqezaemaceleni wathi “Nkosi yami ngisindise ebantwini abangalungile”"
  28,22,"Futhi kwathi lapho elibhekise eMadyan wathi, “Ngifisa ukuthi iNkosi yami ingiholele endleleni eqondile”"
  28,23,"Futhi kwathi lapho esefika emanzini aseMadyan wafica isixuku sabantu siphuzisa (imfuyo) amanzi futhi ngaphandle kwaso (isixuku sabantu) wafica abesifazane ababili ababemise (imihlambiyaboukubaingaphuziuMose) wathi,“kwenzenjani ngani nobabili” bobabili bathi, “angeke siyiphuzise (imihlambi yethu amanzi) kuze kube abelusi basusa (imihlambi yabo) futhi ubaba wethu usekhule kakhulu”"
  28,24,"Ngakho-ke wabaphuzisela bobabili (imihlambi yabo) wayesephenduka eya emthunzini wayesethi, “Nkosi yami ngempela mina nginesidingo sanoma ngabe yini enhle oyehlisele phezu kwami”"
  28,25,"Ngakho-ke oyedwa wabesifazane ababili weza kuyena ehamba ekhophoza wathi owesifazane, “ngempela ubaba wami uyakumema ukuze akunike umvuzo ngokusiphuzisela kwakho (imihlambi) ngakho-ke kwathi lapho esefika kuyena wamxoxela indaba wathi ungesabi uphephile ebantwini abangalungile"
  28,26,"Owesifazane oyedwa kubona bobabili wathi, “Oh baba wami! Mqashe ngempela ungumuntu ongcono kakhulu ukuba umqashe unamandla, wethembekile”"
  28,27,Wathi (uyise wabesifazane ababili) “ngempela mina ngithanda ukuba ushade neyodwa yamadodakazi ami amabili ngesivumelwano sokuba ungisebenzele iminyaka eyisishiyagalombili kepha uma uqeda eyishumi kuyobe kungentando yakho futhi angithandi ukukubeka ebunzimeni uzongifumana ngingomunye wabalungileyo uma uMvelinqangi ethanda
  28,28,Wathi lokho kuphakathi kwami nawe noma ngabe yikuphi kwako kokubili engiyokufeza angeke kubekhona okungenabo ubulungiswa kumina futhi uMvelinqangi ungaphezu kwalokho esikushoyo
  28,29,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho uMose esesiqedile isikhathi esimisiwe futhi esehamba nomndeni wakhe wabona umlilo eceleni kweTur wathi emndenini wakhe, “yimani ngempela mina ngibone umlilo ngingeza kunina nezindaba ezivela kuwona noma isikhuni somlilo ukuze nizifudumeze”"
  28,30,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho esefika kuwona wamenyezwa eceleni langakwe sokudla lesogodi endaweni ebusisiwe esihlahleni Oh Mose! Ngempela mina nginguMvelinqangi iNkosi yemihlaba
  28,31,"Futhi phonsa induku yakho phansi, ngakho-ke kwathi lapho eseyibona inyakaza sengathi iyinyoka waphenduka wabaleka wangabe esabheka emumva Oh Mose! Sondela ungesabi ngempela wena ungomunye wabaphephile"
  28,32,Faka isandla sakho ephaketheni lakho sizophuma simhlophe singenabo ububi futhi sondeza isandla sakho kuwena ukuze uqede ukwesaba lezi yizimpawu ezimbili ezivela eNkosini yakho ziya kuFaro nabaholi bakhe ngempela bona bangabantu abangahloniphi
  28,33,"Wathi (uMose), “Nkosi yami ngempela mina ngabulala umuntu kubona ngakho-ke ngiyesaba ukuthi bazongibulala"
  28,34,Kodwa umfowethu u-Aroni yena ukhuluma kangcono kunami ngakho-ke mthumele kanye nami njengomsizi angiqinise ngempela mina ngiyesaba ukuthi bazongiphika
  28,35,"Wathi, “sizoqinisa ingalo yakho ngomfowenu futhi nobabili sizoninikeza igunya lokuthi bangafinyeleli kunina nobabili ngezimpawu zethu, nina nobabili kanye nanoma ngabe ngubani onilandelayo nobabili niyoba ngabanqobi”"
  28,36,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho uMose esefika kubona nezimpawu zethu ezicacile bathi, “lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngumlingo owenziwe futhi asikaze sizwe ngalokhu kobaba bethu basendulo”"
  28,37,"Futhi uMose wathi, “iNkosi yami yazi kangcono ngalowo owafika nokuhola okuvela kuyona kanye nalowo oyoba nesiphetho esihle empilweni ezayo, ngempela yona ayiziphumelelisi izoni”"
  28,38,Futhi uFaro wathi “Oh baholi! Angazi ukuthi ninaye unkulunkulu ngaphandle kwami ngakho-ke ngibasele (umlilo) we Haman (ukuze wenze izitini) ngobumba bese ungenzela indlu ephakeme ukuze ngigibele ngibone uNkulunkulu kaMose futhi ngempela mina ngicabanga ukuthi yena ungomunye wabaqamba amanga
  28,39,Futhi wayeqhosha yena namabutho akhe ezweni ngokungesilona iqiniso futhi babecabanga ukuthi angeke babuyiselwe kuthina
  28,40,Ngakho-ke samthatha kanye namabutho akhe sabaphonsa olwandle ngakho-ke bheka ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho sezoni
  28,41,Futhi sabenza ukuthi babengabaholi abamemela emlilweni futhi ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo angeke balekelelwe
  28,42,Futhi sabalandelanisa ngesiqalekiso kulomhlaba futhi ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo bona bayokuba ngabanye babavinjelwe emseni kaMvelinqangi
  28,43,"Futhi ngempela samnikeza uMose incwadi emva kokuba sesibhubhise izinkulungwane zasemandulo, ukukhanyiselwa kwabantu nokuholwa kanye nomusa ukuze mhlawumbe bakhumbule"
  28,44,Futhi wawungekho ngaseduzane nentshonalanga ngenkathi senza impoqo kuMose futhi wawungesiyena omunye wofakazi
  28,45,Kepha saziveza izizukulwane sazelulela izikhathi zempilo yazo futhi wawungahlali nabantu baseMidyani ubafundele amavesi ethu kepha yithina esingabathumeli (baleyomyalezo)
  28,46,"Futhi wawungekho eduzane nentaba ngenkathi sasimemeza, kepha ngumusa ovela eNkosini yakho ukuze uxwayise abantu okungazange kufike kubona umxwayisi ngaphambilini kwakho ukuze bakhumbule"
  28,47,"Futhi uma bengase behlelwe okubi ngenxa yalokho okuthunyelwe yizandla zabo ngaphambili bathi, “Nkosi yethu kungani ungasithumelanga kuthina isithunywa ukuze silandele amavesi akho bese siba ngabanye babakholwayo na"
  28,48,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebefikelwa yiqiniso elivela kuthina bathi, “kungani enganikezwanga (izimpawu) ezifana nalezo ezanikezwa uMose na? Ngakube abakholelwa yini kulokho okwanikezwa uMose ngaphambilini” bathi “imilingo emibili omunye welekelela omunye futhi bathi ngempela asikholelwa kukona kokubili”"
  28,49,Ithi “ngakho-ke lethani incwadi evela kuMvelinqangi okuyiyona ehola kangcono kunalezi zombili engizoyilanda uma kungukuthi nina nineqiniso
  28,50,Kepha uma bengakuphenduli ngakho-ke yazi ukuthi kuphela balandela izinkanuko zabo futhi ngubani ophambuke kakhulu kunalowo olandela izinkanuko zakhe ngaphandle kokuholwa okuvela kuMvelinqangi ngempela uMvelinqangi akabaholi abantu abayizoni
  28,51,Futhi ngempela sabathumelela izwi ukuze bakhumbule
  28,52,"Labo esabanikeza incwadi ngaphambilini kwayo, bona bakholelwa kuyona"
  28,53,"Futhi uma befundelwa yona bathi “siyakholelwa kuyona ngempela yona iyiqiniso elivela eNkosini yethu ngempela thina ngaphambilini kwayo, sasingabazinikeleyo ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi"
  28,54,Labo bayonikezwa umvuzo wabo amahlandla amabili ngenxa yokuthi babebekezela besusa okubi ngokuhle futhi bayephana ngaloko esababela kona
  28,55,"Futhi uma bezwa inkulumo embi bayaqhelelana nayo futhi bathi, “okwethu yimisebenzi yethu nokwenu yimisebenzi yenu, ukuthula makube kunina asibathandi abangazi lutho"
  28,56,Ngempela wena awumholi lowo omthandayo kepha nguMvelinqangi ohola lowo amthandayo futhi yena wazi kangcono ngabaholiweyo
  28,57,"Futhi bathi, “uma silandela ukuholwa kanye nawe sizosuswa ezweni lethu” asizange yini sibabekele indawo engcwele ephephile ekulethwa kuyona izithelo eziyizinhlobonhlobo okuyisabelo esivela kuthina kepha iningi labo alazi"
  28,58,Futhi mangaki amadolobha esawabhubhisa ayengazibongi izindlela zawo zokuphila na? Ngakho-ke lezo yizindawo zabo zokuhlala ekungazange kuhlalwe kuzona ngemva kwabo ngaphandle kwesikhashana futhi thina sasiyizindlalifa
  28,59,Futhi iNkosi yakho ayizange iwabhubhise amadolobha kuze kube yilapho ithumela isithunywa kumama wedolobha sibafundela amavesi ethu futhi sasingawabhubhisi amadolobha ngaphandle kokuba uma abantu bawo bonile
  28,60,"Futhi noma ngabe yini enanikezwa yona yinjabulo yempilo yakulomhlaba nomhlobiso wayo futhi noma ngabe yini ekuMvelinqangi ingcono futhi ngasosonke isikhathi ikhona, ngakube aninamqondo yini na"
  28,61,Ngakube lowo esamethembisa isethembiso esihle yena uzohlangana naso njengalowo esamupha injabulo yempilo yalomhlaba besekuthi yena ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo abengomunye walabo abayokujeziswa
  28,62,"Futhi ngosuku ayobabiza ngalo athi, “baphi abahlanganyeli bami labo enaningenzela bona na?”"
  28,63,"Labo izwi elafinyelela kubona liyiqiniso bayothi, “Nkosi yethu naba laba esabaphambukisa, sabaphambukisa njengoba saphambuka uqobo lwethu siveza ukubamsulwa kwethu kuwena akuyithina ababesikhonza”"
  28,64,"Futhi kuyothiwa, “bizani abahlanganyeli benu ngakho-ke bayobamemeza kepha angeke babaphendule futhi bayosibona isijeziso, ukube nje babeholeleke (endleleni eqondile)”"
  28,65,"Futhi ngosuku ayobabiza ngalo bese ethi, “naziphendula kanjani izithunywa na?”"
  28,66,Ngakho-ke izindaba ziyofiphala kubona ngalolosuku angeke bakwazi ukubuzana bodwa
  28,67,Kepha lowo ophendukayo azisole futhi akholwe enze izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo uyokuba ngomunye wabaphumeleleyo
  28,68,"Futhi iNkosi yakho idala noma ngabe yini eyithandayo futhi iyakhetha, akusikona okwabo ukukhetha udumo malube kuMvelinqangi futhi uphakeme ngaphezu kwako konke lokho abamenzela ngako abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni"
  28,69,Futhi iNkosi yakho iyakwazi lokho izifuba zabo ezikufihlayo nalokho ezikuvezayo
  28,70,Futhi yona inguMvelinqangi akukho okunokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwayo udumo lungolwayo ngokokuqala nangokokugcina futhi ukwehlulela kungokwayo futhi niyophindiselwa kuyona
  28,71,Ithi ngakube nibonile yini ukuthi uma uMvelinqangi wayenganenzela ubusuku buqhubeke kuze kube usuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo yimuphi uNkulunkulu ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi onganilethela ukukhanya na? Ngakube anizwa yini na
  28,72,Ithi ngakube nibonile yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi wayenganenzela imini iqhubeke kuze kube usuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo yimuphi uNkulunkulu ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi onganilethela ubusuku eniphumula kubona na? Ngakube aniboni yini na
  28,73,Futhi kusemseni wakhe ukuthi wanenzela ubusuku nemini ukuze niphumule kubona nokuthi nifune umusa wakhe nokuthi nibonge
  28,74,"Nangosuku lapho eyobe ebabiza bese ethi, “baphi abahlanganyeli bami labo enanibenza na”"
  28,75,"Futhi siyokhipha ufakazi kuzona zonke izizwe bese sithi, “lethani ubufakazi benu ngakho-ke bayokwazi ukuthi iqiniso ngelikaMvelinqangi futhi kuyobalahlekela konke lokho ababekuqamba”"
  28,76,"Ngempela uQarun wayengomunye wabantu bakaMose kepha wabahlupha futhi samupha emnothweni izikhiye zawo zingaba ngumthwalo wamadoda aqatha, khumbula ngenkathi abantu bakhe bethi kuyena “ungesasi ngempela uMvelinqangi akabathandi abesasayo"
  28,77,"Kepha funa indawo yokuhlala yempilo ezayo ngalokho uMvelinqangi akunika kona futhi ungayikhohlwa ingxenye yakho kulomhlaba wenze okuhle njengoba uMvelinqangi wenza okuhle kuwena futhi ungafuni ukwenza ukona emhlabeni, ngempela uMvelinqangi akazithandi izoni"
  28,78,"Wathi, “kuphela nginikiwe lokhu ngenxa yolwazi enginalo, wayengazi yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi wazibhubhisa izizukulwane ngaphambilini kwakhe ezazinamandla kunaye futhi zaziziningi kakhulu ngenani futhi angeke zibuzwe izoni ngezono zazo"
  28,79,"Ngakho-ke waphuma waya kubantu bakhe ewubukhazikhazi wathi, “labo abafisa impilo yalomhlaba, Oh! Sifisa sengathi singaba nako konke lokho okwanikwa uQarun ngempela yena unenhlanhla enkulu"
  28,80,Kepha labo ababenikezwe ulwazi bathi “usizi kunina! umvuzo kaMvelinqangi ungcono kunoma ngabe ngubana okholwayo futhi owenza izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo abekho abemukeliswa lokho ngaphandle kwababekezelayo
  28,81,Ngakho-ke sawenza umhlaba ukuthi umgwinye kanye nendlu yakhefuthiwayengenaloiqembuelalizomelekelelaukubhekana noMvelinqangi futhi wayengeke akwazi ukuzivikela
  28,82,"Futhi labo ababefisa isikhundla sakhe ngayizolo baqala bathi, “Oh ngempela! NguMvelinqangi owandisa isabelo kunoma ngabe ngubani amthandayo ezincekwini zakhe noma asinciphise (isabelo), ukube uMvelinqangi wayengenawo umusa kuthina wayezokwenza ukuthi umhlaba usigwinye, Oh labo abangakholwa! angeke baphunyeleliswe"
  28,83,Leyondawo yokuhlala yempilo ezayo siyoyibekela labo abangathandi ukuziphakamisa nokona emhlabeni futhi isiphetho (esihle) esalabo abenza okulungileyo
  28,84,"Noma ngabe ngubani oletha okuhle ngakho-ke okwakhe kuyoba okuhle kunako, futhi noma ngabe ngubani oletha izenzo ezimbi, ngakho-ke angeke abanike umvuzo labo abenza izenzo ezimbi ngaphandle kwalokho ababekwenza"
  28,85,"Ngempela (u-Allah) lowo owenza iQur’an yaba yisibopho kuwena uzokwenza ukuthi uphindele endaweni yokuphindela ithi, “iNkosi yami yazi kabanzi ukuthi ngubani oletha ukuholwa nokuthi ngubani osekudukeni okucacile"
  28,86,"Futhi wawungalindele ukuthi incwadi iyokwembulwa kuwena kepha kungumusa ovela eNkosini yakho, ngakhoke ungabi ngumelekeleli wabangakholwa"
  28,87,"Futhi abangakuvimbeli emavesini ekushumayeleni ngezimpawu kaMvelinqangi emva kokuba esembuliwe kuwena, futhi memela eNkosini yakho futhi ungabi ngomunye wabakhonza izithombe"
  28,88,"Futhi ungambizi omunye unkulunkulu kanye noMvelinqangi akekho onelungelo lokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe, zonke izinto ziyobhubha ngaphandle kobuso bakhe kungokwakhe ukwehlulela futhi niyophindiselwa kuyena"
  29,1,ALIF LAM MEEM
  29,2,"Ngakube abantu bacabanga ukuthi bayekwe bathi, “siyakholwa futhi bona angeke balingwe yini?”"
  29,3,Futhi ngempela sabalinga labo ababengaphambilini kwabo ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi uyabazi labo abaneqiniso futhi uyabazi abaqamba amanga
  29,4,Noma labo abenza izenzo ezimbi bacabanga ukuthi bangasidlula na? okubi yilokho abakwehlulelayo
  29,5,NomangabengubaniowethembaukuhlangananoMvelinqangi ngakho-ke ngempela isikhathi sikaMvelinqangi siyeza futhi yena ungozwayo owaziyo
  29,6,Futhi noma ngabe ngubani ozabalazayo kuphela uzabalazela umphefumulo wakhe ngempela uMvelinqangi akadingi lutho emhlabeni
  29,7,Futhi labo abakholwayo benze imisebenzi elungileyo ngempela siyobasula ububi babo bese sibanika umvuzo omuhle kakhulu kwaloko ababekwenza
  29,8,Futhi siyale umntu ukuthi enze okuhle kubazali bakhe kepha uma bezabalaza ukukwenza ukuthi ungenzele abahlanganyeli ekungikhonzeni lokho ongenalo ulwazi ngako ungabahloniphi bobabili kukumina ukuphindela kwenu bese nginitshela ngalokho enanikwenza
  29,9,Futhi labo abakholwayo bese benza izenzo ezilungileyo ngempela siyobangenisa phakathi kwabalungileyo
  29,10,"Futhi phakathi kwabantu kunalabo abathi, “siyakholwa kuMvelinqangi” kepha uma behlushwa ngenxa kaMvelinqangi bathatha ukulingwa kwabantu njengesijeziso sikaMvelinqangi uma sekufika usizo oluvela eNkosini yakho bathi, “ngempela thina sasikanye nani” akusiyena yini uMvelinqangi owazi kangcono ngalokho okusezifubeni zemihlaba (zabantu namajinn) na"
  29,11,Futhi ngempela uMvelinqangi uyabazi labo abakholwayo futhi ngempela uyabazi abazenzisi (emva kokubalinga)
  29,12,Futhi labo abangakholwa bathi kulabo abakholwayo “landelani indlela yethu ukuze sithwale izono zenu kulapho bona bengeke bathwale lutho lwezono zabo ngempela bona baqamba amanga
  29,13,Futhi ngempela bayoyithwala imithwalo yabo neminye imithwalo kanye nemithwalo yabo futhi ngempela bayobuzwa ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo mayelana nalokho ababekuqamba
  29,14,Futhi ngampela samthumela uNowa ebantwini bakhe wayesehlala phakathi kwabo iminyaka eyinkulungwane ngaphandle kweminyaka engamashumi amahlanu ngakho-ke uzamcolo wabathatha kulapho bona beyizoni
  29,15,Ngakho-ke samsindisa kanye nalabo ababesemkhunjini futhi sakwenza lokho kwaba yisifundo emihlabeni
  29,16,"No-Abraham khumbula ngenkathi ethi kubantu bakhe, “khonzani uMvelinqangi futhi nimesabe lokho kungcono kunina ukube benazi”"
  29,17,"Kuphela nikhonza izithombe esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi futhi niqamba amanga ngempela labo enibakhonzayo esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi abanawo amandla okunika isabelo, ngakho-ke sifuneni kuMvelinqangi isabelo futhi mkhonzeni, futhi nimbonge niyophindiselwa kuyena"
  29,18,Futhi uma niwuphika (umyalezo) ngempela izizwe zawuphika ngaphambilini kwenu futhi awukho umsebenzi ophezu kwesithunywa ngaphandle kokudlulisela umyalezo ocacile
  29,19,Aniboni yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi uyisungula kanjani indalo bese eyiveza kabusha ngempela lokho kulula kuMvelinqangi
  29,20,"Ithi, “hambani ezweni nibone ukuthi wayisungula kanjani indalo bese uMvelinqangi eveza indalo yempilo ezayo, ngempela uMvelinqangi unamandla okwenza zonke izinto"
  29,21,Ujezisa noma ngabe ngubani omthandayo futhi abenomusa kunoma ngabe ngubani omthandayo futhi niyophindiselwa kuyena
  29,22,Futhi nina aniphunyukile lapha emhlabeni nasezulwini futhi ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi aninaye omunye umvikeli nomsizi
  29,23,Futhi labo abangakholelwa emavesini kaMvelinqangi nasekuhlanganeni naye labo-ke abanalo ithemba emseni wami futhi labo okwabo yisijeziso esibuhlungu
  29,24,"Ngakho-ke ayibangalutho impendulo yabantu bakhe ngaphandle kokuthi bathi “mbulaleni noma nimshise”, kepha uMvelinqangi wamsindisa emlilweni ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu ebantwini abakholwayo"
  29,25,"Futhi wathi, “kuphela nizithathele izithombe esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi ngenxa yobungane phakathi kwenu empilweni yalomhlaba besekuthi ngosuku lokuvula kwabafikeleyo abanye benu baphike abanye futhi abanye benu bayoqalekisa abanye futhi indawo yenu yokuhlala kuyoba ngumlilo futhi angeke nibe nabo abasizi”"
  29,26,"Wakholwa kuye uLothi wayesethi, “ngempela mina ngizoba ngoshiya ikhaya lami ngiye eNkosini yami ngempela yona iphakeme ngamandla inobuhlakani”"
  29,27,Futhi (u-Abraham) samupha u-Isaka noJakobe futhi enzalweni yakhe sabeka ubuphrofethi kanye nencwadi futhi samnikeza umvuzo wakhe kulomhlaba futhi ngempela yena empilweni ezayo uyokuba ngomunye wabalungileyo
  29,28,"NoLothi khumbula ngenkathi ethi ebantwini bakhe, “ngempela nina nenza ukukhohlakala eningakaze nedlulwe ngisho noma umuntu oyedwa kukona emihlabeni"
  29,29,Ngakube nina niza emadodeni futhi niphazamisa emgaqweni (niphanga izihambi) futhi emhlanganweni wenu nenza izenzo ezimbi ngakho-ke yayingelutho impendulo yabantu bakhe ngaphandle kokuthi bathi “silethele isijeziso sikaMvelinqangi uma kungukuthi wena ungomunye wabaneqiniso
  29,30,"Wathi, “Nkosi yami ngelekelele ebantwini abayizoni”"
  29,31,Futhi kwathi lapho sezifika izithunywa zethu ku-Abraham nezindaba ezinhle zathi “ngempela thina sizobabhubhisa abantu baledolobha ngempela abantu balo babeyizoni”
  29,32,"Wathi, “ngempela kulona kunoLothi” zathi “thina sazi kangcono ukuthi ngubani okulona ngempela sizomsindisa kanye nomndeni wakhe ngaphandle konkosikazi wakhe wayengomunye wabasalela ngemumva”"
  29,33,Futhi kwathi lapho izithunywa zethu sezifika waba lusizi ngenxa yazo wahamba elusizi ngenxa yazo zathi “ungesabi futhi ungaphatheki kabi ngempela thina sizokusindisa kanye nomndeni wakho ngaphandle konkosikazi wakho ungomunye wabasalela ngemumva”
  29,34,Ngempela thina siyokwehlisela phezu kwabantu balelidolobha isijeziso esivela ezulwini ngenxa yokuthi bebephula umthetho
  29,35,Futhi ngempela salushiya kulona uphawu olucacile kubantu abaqondayo
  29,36,"NaseMidyanisathumelaumfowabo uShuaybwathi,“Oh bantu bami! khonzani uMvelinqangi nithembe (umvuzo) wosuku lokugcina futhi ningenzi ububi ezweni njengezikhohlakali”"
  29,37,Ngakho-ke bamphika basebethathwa ukuzamazama komhlaba basala bedindilizile ezindlini zabo
  29,38,"No-A’D noThamund (ukubuyiswa kwabo) kwacaca kunina ezindlini zabo futhi uSathane wayenza yabukeka imihle kubona\timisebenzi yabo wayesebavimbela endleleni (eqondile) kulapho bebhekile"
  29,39,NoQarun noFaro noHaman futhi ngempela uMose wafika kubona nezimpawu ezicacile kepha bazikhukhumeza emhlabeni futhi babengeke baphunyuke (esijezisweni)
  29,40,Ngakho-ke ngamunye sambamba ngesono sakhe phakathi kwabo kunalabo esabathumelela ngesichotho futhi phakathi kwabo kunalabo abathathwa ngumsindo owesabekayo futhi phakathi kwabo kunalabo esabagwinyisa ngomhlabathi futhi phakathi kwabo kunalabo esabaminzisa futhi akusiyena uMvelinqangi owenza okungalungile kubona kepha imiphefumulo yabo eyenza okungalungile
  29,41,Isibonelo salabo abathatha (onkulunkulu bamanga) njengabavikeli esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi sifana nesicabucabu esakha indlu futhi ngempela ezindlini eziyizintengentenge kakhulu yindlu yesicabucabu ukube nje babazi
  29,42,Ngempela uMvelinqangi wazi noma ngabe yini abayimemezayo esikhundleni sakhe futhi yena uphakekeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  29,43,Futhi lezo yizibonelo esizenzela abantu futhi akekho oziqondayo ngaphandle kwabafundile
  29,44,"UMvelinqangi wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngeqiniso, ngempela kulokho kunophawu kwabakholwayo"
  29,45,"Funda lokho okwembulwa kuwena okusencwadini futhi wenze umthandazo, ngempela umthandazo wenqabela ezonweni nasezenzweni ezimbi futhi ngempela inkumbulo kaMvelinqangi yinkulu kakhulu, futhi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi lokho enikwenzayo"
  29,46,"Futhi ningaphikisani nabantu bencwadi ngaphandle kwaleyo (ndlela) engcono kakhulu, ngaphandle kwalabo abenza okungalungile phakathi kwabo futhi yithini, “siyakholwa kulokho okwambulwa kuthina nokwambulwa kunina futhi uNkulunkulu wethu noNkulunkulu wenu munye futhi thina siyazithoba ngaphansi kwentando yakhe"
  29,47,"Futhi sayembula kanjalo kuwena incwadi ngakho-ke labo esabanika incwadi bayakhokhelwa kuyona futhi phakathi kwalaba kunalabo abakholelwa kuyona, abekho abawaphikayo amavesi ethu ngaphandle kwabangakholwa"
  29,48,"Futhi awuzange uyifunde enye incwadi ngaphambilini kwayo lencwadi noma uyibhale ngesandla sakho sokudla, kepha abaqambi bamanga basekungabazeni"
  29,49,"Qhabo! Wona angamavesi acacile ezinhliziyweni zalabo abesekwa ngolwazi, futhi abekho abawaphikayo amavesi ethu ngaphandle kwabayizoni"
  29,50,"Futhi bathi, “kungani zingahliselwanga phansi kuyena izimpawu ezivela eNkosini yakhe na?” ithi “kuphela izimpawu zikuMvelinqangi futhi kuphela mina ngingumxwayisi ogqamile”"
  29,51,"Akwanele yini kubona ukuthi thina sembule kuwena incwadi abafundelwa yona, ngempela kulokho kunomusa nesikhumbuzo kubantu abakholwayo"
  29,52,"Ithi, “Wanele uMvelinqangi ukuba ngufakazi phakathi kwami nani wazi noma ngabe yini esemazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi labo abakholelwa emangeni futhi abangakholelwa kuMvelinqangi labo – ke bona bangabalahlekelweyo"
  29,53,"Futhi bayakucela ukuthi usheshisa isijeziso, Ukuba kwakungesingenxa yesikhathi esinqunyiwe sasiyofika kubona isijeziso, futhi sasiyofika kubona bengazelele ngokuphazima kweso kulapho bona bengaboni"
  29,54,Bayakucela ukuthi usheshise isijeziso futhi ngempela isihogo siyobazungeza abangakholwa
  29,55,Ngosuku lapho isijeziso siyokubamboza siqhamuka ngaphezulu kwabo nangaphansi kwezinyawo zabo futhi uyothi”yizwani enanivamise ukukwenza
  29,56,Oh zinceku zami! Ezikholwayo ngempela umhlaba wami ubanzi Ngakho-ke khonzani mina ngedwa
  29,57,Yonke imiphefumulo iyozwa ukufa bese nibuyiselwa kuthina
  29,58,"Futhi labo abakholwayo futhi abenza imisebenzi elungileyo ngempela siyobanika izindawo zokuhlala ezulwini (esivandeni) okugeleza ngaphansi kwaso imifula bayohlala lapho phakathi ingunaphakade, umvuzo omuhle kakhulu wabasebenzayo"
  29,59,Labo ababekezelayo futhi abathembela eNkosini yabo
  29,60,Futhi zingaki izidalwa ezingaziphethe izabelo zazo na? NguMvelinqangi ozipha isabelo kanye nani futhi yena ungozwayo owaziyo
  29,61,Futhi ukuba ubuzobabuza ukuthi ngubani owadala amazulu nomhlaba futhi wabeka ilanga nenyanga na? Bayothi ngempela “nguMvelinqangi kwenzeka kanjani ukuthi bachezuke (endleleni eqondile) na?”
  29,62,"UMvelinqangi welulela isipho kunoma ngabe ngubani amthandayo ezincekwini zakhe futhi ambeke esimweni sobuphofu, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyisazi sazozonke izinto"
  29,63,"Futhi uma ubabuza ukuthi ngubani owehlisela phansi amanzi (imvula) avela esibhakabhakeni bese evusa ngawo umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo na? ngempela bayothi, “nguMvelinqangi”yithi, “udumo malube kuMvelinqangi” kepha iningi labo alinawo umqondo"
  29,64,"Futhi impilo yalomhlaba ayiyilutho ngaphandle kokuthi iyinjabulo nomdlalo, futhi ngempela ikhaya lempilo ezayo lingelempilo (yangunaphakade) ukube nje bebazi"
  29,65,Ngakho-ke uma sebegibela emkhujini babiza uMvelinqangi ngobuqotho inkolo ingeyakhe (kuphela) kepha kwathi lapho ebasindisa ebafikisa emhlabeni kwaba yilapho bona bemenzela abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni
  29,66,"Ukuze bangakubongi lokho esabapha kona futhi bazithokozise, kepha bayokwazi"
  29,67,Ababoni yini ukuthi sayenza indawo engcwele yaphepha kulapho bethathwa ngenkani abantu emaceleni abo ngakube bakholelwa enkohlakalweni bangakholelwa emseni ka Mvelinqangi na
  29,68,Futhi ngubani ongenabulungiswa kakhulu kunalowo oqambela uMvelinqangi amanga noma ophika iqiniso kulapho selifikile kuyena na? Akusona yini isihogo indawo yokuhlala abangakholwayo na
  29,69,Futhi labo abazabalaza kanzima (endleleni) yethu ngempela siyobaholela endleleni yethu futhi ngempela uMveleinqangi ukanye nabenzi bokuhle
  30,1,ALIF LAM MEEM
  30,2,AbaseRoma banqontshwa
  30,3,Ezweni eliseduzane futhi bona emva kokuhlulwa kwabo bayonqoba
  30,4,"Eminyakeni emibalwa, isinqumo singesikaMvelingangi ngemuva nangaphambili futhi ngalolosuku amakholwa ayojabula"
  30,5,Ngenxa yosizo lukaMvelinqangi usiza noma ngabe ngubani amthandayo futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unesihawu
  30,6,"Isethembiso sika Mvelinqangi, uMvelinqangi akasephuli isethembiso sakhe kepha iningi labantu alazi"
  30,7,"Bazi okubonakalayo kwempilo yalomhlaba, futhi bona abayinakile impilo ezayo"
  30,8,"Abacabangi yini uqobo lwabo ukuthi uMvelinqangi akawadalanga amazulu nomhlaba kanye nako konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili. Ngaphandle\tkweqiniso nangokwesikhathi esimisiweyo na? futhi ngempela iningi labantu liyiziphiki ngokuhlangana neNkosi yabo"
  30,9,"Abahambanga yini emhlabeni ukuze babone ukuthi sasinjani isiphethosalaboababengaphambilinikwabona?Babenamandla ngaphezu kwabo futhi babewulima umhlabathi futhi bahlala kuwona isikhathi eside ngokwedlulele kunokuhlala kwalaba, futhi zafika kubona izithunywa zabo nezimpawu ezicacile, ngakho-ke kwangungesiyena uMvelinqangi owenza okungalungile kubona kepha yimiphefumulo yabo eyenza okungalungile"
  30,10,Khona manjalo isiphetho salabo ababenza okubi sasisibi ngokuba babewaphika amavesi kaMvelinqangi futhi babewenza inhlekisa
  30,11,UMvelinqangi usungula indalo bese eyiphinda bese nibuyiselwa kuyena
  30,12,Futhi ngosuku ekuyofika ngalo ihora izoni ziyopheleliswa ngethemba
  30,13,Futhi angeke babenabo abakhulumeli phakathi kwezithixo zabo futhi bayoziphika izithixo zabo
  30,14,"Futhi ngosuku ekuyofika ngalo ihora, ngalolosuku bayohlukaniswa"
  30,15,Ngakho-ke labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo bayokuba sengadini yentokozo
  30,16,Futhi labo abangakholwanga abaphika amavesi ethu kanye nokuhlangana kwempilo ezayo labo bayolethwa esijezisweni
  30,17,Ngakho-ke udumo malube kuMvelinqangi ngenkathi ningena kusihlwa nangenkathi ningena ekuseni
  30,18,Futhi udumo lungolwakho emazulwini nasemhlabeni nasebusuku nasemini
  30,19,Uveza ophilayo kofileyo futhi uveza ofile kophilayo futhi uphilisa umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo futhi niyovezwa kanjalo
  30,20,Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe (uMvelinqangi) ukuthi wanidala ngothuli kwase kuthi uma nina seningabantu nahlakazeka
  30,21,"Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe ukuthi wanidalela amakhosikazi phakathi kwenu ukuze niphumule kuwona futhi phakathi kwenu wabeka uthando nomusa, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu (nezifundo) ebantwini abacabangayo"
  30,22,"Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe yindalo yamazulu nomhlaba nokwehlukahlukana kwezilimi zenu kanye nemibala yenu, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kwabafundile"
  30,23,"Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe ukulala kwenu ebusuku nasemini nokufuna kwenu ububele bakhe, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu ebantwini abezwayo"
  30,24,"Futhi oluye lwezimpawu zakhe ukuthi unikhombisa umbani wokwesaba nowokunika ithemba futhi wehlisela phansi amanzi (imvula) evela esibhakabhakeni bese ephilisa ngayo umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu ebantwini abanomqondo"
  30,25,Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe wukuthi izulu nomhlaba kumile ngomyalelo wakhe kuyothi uma enibiza ubizo olulodwa emhlabeni bheka! Nina niyoza
  30,26,Futhi ungowakhe noma ngabe ngubani osemazulwini nasemhlabeni bonke bayamhlonipha
  30,27,"Futhi nguyena osungula indalo bese eyiphinda, futhi lokho kulula kakhulu kuyena, futhi umfanekiso wakhe uphakeme kakhulu emazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla anobuhlakani"
  30,28,"Wanenzela isibonele emiphefumulweni yenu. Ngakube ninabo yini kulabo abasezandleni zenu zangakwezokudla abahlanganyeli kulokhu esabela kona ngakho-ke nina niyalingana kukona niyabesaba njengoba nesabana nina uqobo lwenu, siwachaza kanjalo ngokucacile amavesi kubantu abanomqondo"
  30,29,"Kepha labo abangalungile balandela izifiso zabo ngaphandle kolwazi, ngakho-ke ngubani ongahola lowo uMvelinqangi amshiye ekudukeni na? futhi angeke babenabo abelekeleli"
  30,30,"Ngakho-ke bhekisa ubuso bakho enkolweni ngobuqotho, indalo kaMvelinqangi okuyiyona adalela abantu kuyona ayingashintshwa indalo kaMvelinqangi, leyo yinkolo eqondile kepha iningi labantu alazi"
  30,31,"Wanidala ngendlela yokuthi njalo niphendukele kuye ngokuzisola, futhi nimesabe futhi nenze umthandazo futhi ningabi ngabanye balabo abenzela uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni"
  30,32,"Owalabo abahlukanisa inkolo yabo babe ngamaqembu, iqembu neqembu lijabulela loko elinako"
  30,33,Futhi uma inhlupheko ibathinta abantu babiza iNkosi yabo bephendukela kuyona ngokuzisola besekuthi uma ibazwisa umusa wayo kubeyilapho iqembu phakathi kwabo lenzela iNkosi yalo abahlanganyeli ekuyikhonzeni
  30,34,"Ukuze bangabongi ngalokho esabapha kona, ngakho-ke zithokoziseni (okwesikhashana) kepha nizokwazi"
  30,35,Noma ngabe selehlisela phansi kubona igunya (incwadi) ekhuluma ngalokho ababenzela ngakho uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli na
  30,36,Futhi kwathi lapho sesibazwisa abantu umusa bawuthokozela futhi uma behlelwa okubi ngenxa yalokho okulethwe ngaphambili yizandla zabo bheka! baphelelwa yithemba
  30,37,Ababoni yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi isabelo uselulela noma ngabe ngubani amthandayo futhi asinciphise (kunoma ngabe ngubani amthandayo) ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu ebantwini abakholwayo
  30,38,Ngakho-ke nikeza isihlobo okusifanele noswele kanye nesihambilokhokuhlekulaboabafunaubusobukaMvelinqangi futhi bayilabo abayophumelela
  30,39,"Futhi noma ngabe yini eniphisana ngayo njengesipho ukuze kwandeengcebweniyabantungakho-keayandikuMvelinqangi futhi noma ngabe yini eniyinikelayo njengeZakaah (ingxenye yengcebo ekhokhwa kwabampofu) nifisa ubuso bukaMvelinqangi, ngakho-ke labo bayophindaphindelwa kaningi"
  30,40,"Umvelinqangi nguyena owanidala wayeseninika isabelo futhi uyokwenza ukuthi nife bese eniphilisa, ngakube ukhona yini phakathi kwabahlanganyeli (izithombeni) zenu ongenza okuthize okufana nalokhu na? Udumo malube kuye futhi uphakeme ngaphezu kwalokho abakuhlanganisa naye"
  30,41,"Ububi bavela ezweni nasolwandle ngenxa yalokho okwavunwa yizandla zabantu, ukuze abenze ukuthi bezwe ingxenye yalokho ababekwenza ukuze babuye"
  30,42,"Yithi, “hambani ezweni bese niyabona ukuthi sasinjani isiphethosalaboababengaphambilini, iningilabolaliyizikhonzi zezithombe”"
  30,43,"Ngakho-ke bhekisa ubuso bakho enkolweni eqondile ngaphambi kokuba kufike usuku oluvela kuMvelinqangi akekho ongalugwema, ngalolosuku bayohlukaniswa"
  30,44,Noma ngabe ngubani ongakholwa uyohlukumezeka ngokungakholwa kwakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani owenza imisebenzi emihle elungileyo ngakho-ke balungiselela imiphefumulo yabo indawo enhle
  30,45,"Ukuze abanike umvuzo emseni wakhe labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezinhle ezilungeleyo, ngempela yena akabathandi abangakholwa"
  30,46,Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe ukuthi uthumela imimoya ithwele izindaba ezinhle futhi anizwise emseni wakhe nokuthi imikhumbi ihambe ngemponqo yakhe nokuthi nifune umusa wakhe ukuze nibe nokubonga
  30,47,Futhi ngempela sazithumela ngaphambilini kwakho izithunywa ebantwini bazo zafika kubona neziqinisekiso ezicacile sabe sesiyaziphindisela kulabo abayizoni futhi kufanelekile kuthina ukulekelela abakholwayo
  30,48,"UMvelinqangi nguyena othumela imimoya ukuze iphakamise amafu bese ewandlala esibhakabhakeni ngokuthanda kwakhe futhi uwenza izicucu bese ubona imvula iphuma phakathi kwawo, ngakho-ke uma eseyehlisele phezu kwalowo amthandayo ezincekwini zakhe bheka! zona ziyajabula"
  30,49,Futhi ngaphambi kokuba yehliselwe phezu kwabo ngaphambilini kwayo ngempela babephelelwe yithemba
  30,50,"Ngakho-ke bheka izimpawu zomusa kaMvelinqangi ukuthi uwuvusa kanjani umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo, ngempela lowo uyokuba ngumvusi wabafileyo futhi yena unamandla ngaphezu kwezinto zonke"
  30,51,Futhi uma sithumela umoya bese bewubona uphuzi ngempela bazoduka emva kwalokho bangakholwa
  30,52,Ngakho-ke ngempela wena awukwazi ukwenza abafile bezwe futhi awukwazi ukwenza izithuli zizwe ukumenyezwa kulapho ziphenduka zibheka emuva
  30,53,"Futhi wena awusiyena umholi wezimpumputhe ekudukeni kwazo, awenzi ukuthi bezwe ngaphandlle kwalabo abakholelwa amavesini ethu kulapho bona bezithobile ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi"
  30,54,NguMvelinqangi owanidala (esimweni) sobuntekenteke emuva kobuntekenteke wenza amandla emva kwamandla wayesenza ubuntekenteke nezinwele ezimpunga. Udala noma ngabe yini ayithandayo futhi yena uyisazi ungusomandla
  30,55,Futhi ngosuku ekuyofika ngalo ihora izoni ziyofunga ukuthi azihlalanga ngaphandle kwesikhathi esiyihora. Kanjalo zididisiwe ngasosonke isikhathi
  30,56,"Futhi labo abanikwa ulwazi nokholo bayothi, “ngempela nahlala ngokunqunywe nguMvelinqangi kuze kube usuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo ngakho-ke yilo lolusuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo, kepha nina naningazi"
  30,57,Ngakho-ke ngalolosuku labo ababeyizoni izaba labo angeke lisize ngalutho angeke banikwe ithuba (lokwenza okulungileyo)
  30,58,Futhi ngempela sabenzela abantu zonke izibonelo kuleQur’an futhi uma ubalethela uphawu noma isiqiniseko ngempela labo abangakholwanga bangathi “nina aniyilutho ngaphandle kwabalandeli benkohliso”
  30,59,Ngakho ke uzivala kanjalo uMvelinqangi izinhliziyo zalabo abangazi
  30,60,Ngakho-ke bekezela ngempela isethembiso sikaMvelinqangi siyiqiniso futhi abangakudumazi inhliziyo labo abangenako ukuqiniseka enkolweni
  31,1,ALIF LAM MEEM
  31,2,Lawa ngamavesi encwadi enobuhlakani
  31,3,Ukuholwa nomusa kwabenzi bokuhle
  31,4,Labo abenza umthandazo futhi abakhokha izakaah (ingxenye yengcebo ekhokhwa kwabampofu) futhi bona baqinisekile ngokukholelwa empilweni ezayo
  31,5,Labo-ke basekuholweni okuvela eNkosini yabo futhi labo bangabaphumeleleyo
  31,6,"Futhi phakathi kwabantu kunalowo othenga inkulumo eyize ukuze adukise (ngayo abantu) endleleni kaMvelinqangi ngaphandle kolwazi futhi ayenze inhlekisa, labo-ke okwabo yisijeziso esidumazayo"
  31,7,Futhi uma efundelwa amavesi ethu uyafulathela ngokuzigqaja kube sengathi angakwenza kube sengathi ezindlebeni zakhe zombili kunobuthuli ngakho-ke mtshele ngesijeziso esibuhlungu
  31,8,Ngempela labo abakholwayo futhi abenza imisebenzi emihle okwabo yizivande zenjabulo
  31,9,"Bahlale khona ingunaphakade, isethembiso sikamvelinqangi siyiqiniso futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani"
  31,10,Wadala amazulu angenazo izisekelo enizibonayo futhi wabeka izintaba emhlabeni hleze uzamazame nani futhi wasakaza kuwona zonke izihlobo zezilwane futhi sehlisela phansi amanzi avela esibhakabhakeni sabe sesikhulisa kuwona zonke izihlobo (zezithombo) ezingambili ezinhle
  31,11,"Lena yindalo kaMvelinqangi ngakho-ke ngikhombiseni ukuthi badalani labo ngaphandle (kwendalo) yakhe, qhabo izoni zisekudukeni okugqamile"
  31,12,Futhi ngempela samupha ubuhlakani uLuqman ukhuthi makabonge uMvelinqangi futhi noma ngabe ngubani obangayo kuphela ubongela umphefumulo wakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani ongabongi ngakho-ke ngempela uMvelinqangi akadingi lutho ufanelwe ukudunyiswa
  31,13,Futhi (khumbula) ngenkathi uLuqman ethi endodaneni yakhe ngenkathi eyeluleka “Oh ndodana yami! Ungamenzeli uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni ngempela ukwenzela uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni kungukona okukhulu ngempela”
  31,14,"Futhi samyala umuntu ukuthi enze okuhle kubona bobabili abazali bakhe, unina wayemkhulelwa ngobuthakathaka nangobunzima phezu kobuthakathaka nobunzima, ukukhumulwa kwakhe (ebeleni) kuseminyakeni emibili, bonga mina (Mvelinqangi) kanye nabazali bakho bobabili kukumina ukufinyelela kokugcina"
  31,15,Futhiumabezabalazakanyenaweukukwenzaukuthiungenzele abahlanganyeli ekungikhonzeni lokho ongenalo ulwazi ngako ngakho-ke bobabili ungabahloniphi futhi gcina ubudlelwano obumnene nabo bobabili kulomhlaba futhi landela indlela yalowo ozisolayo kumina ngakho-ke kukumina ukuphindela kwenu bese nginitshela ngalokhu ananikwenza
  31,16,"Oh ndodana yami! Noma ngabe yini engangesisindo sohlamvu lwemastad noma ngabe kusedwalweni noma kusemazulwini noma kusemhlabeni uMvelinqangi uyoza nako, ngempela uMvelinqangi umnene uyazi"
  31,17,Oh Ndodana yami! Yenza umthandazo futhi wenze okuhle okulungileyo wenqabele okubi futhi ubekezelele noma ngabe yini ekuvelelayo ngempela lokho ngeminye yemiyalezo (yezeluleko) ezibalulekile
  31,18,Futhi ungabuphenduleli ubuso bakho kubantu ngokwedelela Futhi ungahambi ezweni ngokuqholosha ngempela uMvelinqangi akabathandi bonke abaqholoshayo abazidlayo
  31,19,Futhi zithobe ekuhambeni kwakho futhi wehlise izwi lakho (uma ukhuluma) ngempela ukubhonga okubi kakhulu ukubhonga kwembongolo
  31,20,Aniboni yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi wenza noma yini esemazulwini yanithobela nanoma yini esemhlabeni futhi waphelelisa umusa wakhe phezu kwenu ngokugqamile nangokufihlekile futhi phakathi kwabantu kunalowo owenza impikiswano ngoMvelinqangi Ngaphandle kolwazi noma ngokuholwa noma ngencwadi ekhanyayo
  31,21,Futhi uma kuthiwa kubona landelani lokho okwembulwa nguMvelinqangi bathi qha silandela lokho esafica obaba bethu bekukona yize noma ngabe usathane ebamemela esijezisweni somlilo nizobalandela na
  31,22,Futhi noma ngabe ngubani othobisa ubuso bakhe kuMvelinqangi futhi yena engumenzi wokuhle ngempela ubambelele esibambelelweni esiqinile futhi sikuMvelinqangi isiphetho sezindaba
  31,23,"Futhi noma ngabe ngubani ongakholwa akungakuphakathi kabi ukungakholwa kwakhe, kukuthina ukubuyela kwabo bese sibatshela ngalokho abebekwenza ngempela uMvelinqangi uyisazi salokho okusezifubeni"
  31,24,Sibathokozisa okwesikhashane bese sibaphoqelela esijezisweni esinzima
  31,25,Futhi uma ubabuza ukuthi ngubani owadala amazulu nomhlaba? Ngempela bayothi “nguMvelinqangi” ithi udumo malube kuMvelinqangi kepha iningi labo alazi
  31,26,IngelikaMvelinqangi noma ngabe yini esemazulwini nasemhlabeni ngempela uMvelinqangi akadingi lutho ufanelwe ukudunyiswa
  31,27,"Futhi ukube zonke izihlahla emhlabeni zazingamapeni, nolwandle nezinye izilwandle eziyisikhombisa ezenezeleliwe emva kwalo (njengoyinki wokubhala amazwi kaMvelinqangi) amazwi ka Mvelinqangi ayengeke aphelele. Ngempela uMvelinqangi uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani"
  31,28,"Ukudalwa kwenu nokuvuswa kwenu kwabafileyo akuyilutho kepha kunjengomphefumulo owodwa, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyezwa uyabona"
  31,29,Awuboni yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi wenza ukuthi ubusuku bungene osukwini futhi wenza ukuthi usuku lungene ebusukwini futhi wenza ilanga nenyanga ngakunye kuhamba kuze kube yisikhathi esinqunyiwe nokuthi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi lokho enikwenzayo na
  31,30,"Lokhu kungenxa yokuthi uMvelinqangi uyiqiiso nokuthi konke lokho abakumemezayo esikhundleni sakhe kungamanga nokuthi yena uphakeme, mkhulu"
  31,31,"Awuboni yini ukuthi imikhumbi ihamba olwandle ngomusa kaMvelinqangi ukuze anikhombise okunye kwezimpawu zakhe na? Ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kubona bonke ababekezelayo, ababongayo"
  31,32,"Futhi uma bembozwa yigagasi libanjengomthunzi bamemeza uMvelinqangi beqotho kuye ngokholo, kepha uma esebasindisile wababeka emhlabathini, ngakho-ke phakathi kwabo kunalabo abamaphakathi (abanqikazayo ukuthi iyiphi indlela ekufanele bayilandele) futhi abekho abawaphikayo amavesi ethu ngaphandle kwabo bonke abasalela ngemumva abangabongi"
  31,33,"(Oh Bantu! Yesabani iNkosi yenu futhi nesabe usuku lapho engekho ubaba oyokwezuzela indodana yakhe futhi ayikho indodana eyokwezuzela uyise utho, ngempela isethembiso sikaMvelinqangi siyiqiniso ngakho-ke ningayivumeli impilo yalomhlaba inikhohlise futhi ningamvumeli umkhohlisi omkhulu usathane) anikhohlise ngoMvelinqangi"
  31,34,"Ngempela uMvelinqangi unolwazi lwehora futhi wehlisela phansi imvula futhi uyakwazi lokho okusezizalweni futhi akekho noma munye owaziyo ukuthi uzotholani kusasa. Futhi akekho owaziyo ukuthi uyofela komuphi umhlaba. Ngempela uMvelinqangi uyazi, welumukile"
  32,1,ALIF LAAM MEEM
  32,2,Isambulo sencwadi ekungenakungabaza kuyo ivela eNkosini yemihlaba
  32,3,"Noma bathi wayiqamba qhabo! Yona iyiqiniso elivela eNkosini yakho ukuze uxwayise abantu ekungazange kufike kubona umxwayisi ngaphambilini kwakho, ukuze baholeleke (endleleni eqondile)"
  32,4,"UMvelinqangi nguyena owadala amazulu nomhlaba kanye nako konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ngezinsuku eziyisithupha wayesezibeka esihlalweni sobukhosi, aninaye omunye umvikela nomncengeli ngaphandle kwakhe anikhumbuli yini na"
  32,5,"Uhlela udaba kusuka ezulwini kuya emhlabeni bese elukhuphukisela kuyena ngosuku, isilinganiso sako esiyiminyaka eyinkulungwane njengoba nibala"
  32,6,Leso yisazi sokungabonwayo kanye nokubonwayo esiphakeme ngamandla esinesihawu
  32,7,Okunguyena owenza zazinhle kakhulu izinto azidalayo wayesesungula indalo yomuntu ngothuli
  32,8,Wayesenza inzalo yakhe ngesidoda esiyamanzi anyanyekayo (akhululwa ngumuntu wesilisa nowesifazane uma besesimweni sokuhlangana)
  32,9,Wayesemenza ngendlela efanelekile waphefumulela kuyena ngomphefumulo wakhe futhi wanenzela ukuzwa (amadlebe) nokubona (amehlo) nezinhliziyo kuncane lokho enikubongayo
  32,10,"Futhi bathi, “Uma sesidukile emhlabeni ngakube siyoba yindalo entsha yini na?” kepha bona bayakuphika ukuhlangana neNkosi yabo"
  32,11,"Ithi, “izokwenza ukuthi nife ingelosi yokufa okuyiyona ebekelwe ukuthi inigade bese nibuyiselwa eNkosini yenu”"
  32,12,"Futhi uma ungazibona izoni zigobise amakhanda azo ngaphambili kweNkosi yazo (zithi), “Nkosi yethu sibonile futhi sizwile ngakho-ke siphindisele emumva sizokwenza imisebenzi emihle elungileyo ngempela singamakholwa ngokuqinisekileyo"
  32,13,Ukuba sasithanda sasizonikeza yonke imiphefumulo ukuholwa kwayo kepha izwi eliyiqiniso livela kuthina ukuthi siyogcwalisa isihogo ngamaJinn kanye nabantu ndawonye
  32,14,Ngakho-keyizwaningenxayokuthinakukhohlwaukuhlangana ngalolusuku lwenu ngempela (nathi) sinikhohliwe futhi yizwani isijeziso esingapheliyo ngenxa yalokho enanikwenza
  32,15,Kuphela abakholelwa emavesini ethu yilapho okuthi uma bekhunjuziswa ngawo bawe phansi bazithobe futhi badumise ukuphakama kweNkosi yabo kulapho bona bengazigabisi
  32,16,Izinhlangothi zabo zishiya imibhede (yabo) bememeza iNkosi yabo ngokwesaba nangethemba futhi basebenzisa (banikela) kulokhu esibabele kona
  32,17,Ngakho-ke awukho umphefumulo owaziyo ukuthi yini eyifihlelwe bona engumvuzo othokozisa ihlo ngenxa yalokho ababekwenza
  32,18,Ngakube lowo oyikholwa uyefana yini nalowo oyisaphulamthetho na? Cha abalingani
  32,19,Futhi labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo okwabo yizivande zokuhlala njengenjabulo ngenxa yalokho ababekwenza
  32,20,Futhi labo abephula umthetho indawo yabo yokuhlala kuyoba ngumlilo. Ngasosonke isikhathi uma befisa ukuphuma kuwona bayophindiselwa phakathi kuwona futhi kuyothiwa kubona yizwani isijeziso somlilo okuyisona nina enanisiphika
  32,21,Futhi ngempela siyobazwisa isijeziso esincane ngaphambi kwesijeziso esikhulu ukuze (bayeke ukona)
  32,22,Futhi ngubani ongalungile kakhulu kunalowo okhunjuziswa ngamavesi eNkosi yakhe bese eyawafulathela ngempela siyoziphindisela kwabayizoni
  32,23,Futhi ngempela samnikeza uMose incwadi ngakho-ke ningabi sekungabazeni ekuhlanganeni nayo futhi sayenza yaba ukuhola kubantwana bakwa Israyeli
  32,24,Futhi sabeka abaholi phakathi kwabo abahola ngempoqo yethu kulapho bebekezela futhi babeqinisekile ngamavesi ethu
  32,25,Ngempela iNkosi yakho iyokwehlulela phakathi kwabo ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo ngalokho ababephikisana kukona
  32,26,"Akusikona yini ukuholwa kubona ukuthi zingaki izizukulwane esazibhubhisa ngaphambilini kwabo abahamba ezindlini zazo, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu, ngakube abezwa yini na"
  32,27,"Ababoniyiniukuthisathumelaamanziemhlabeniongugwadile sabe sesiveza ngawo izitshalo ezidliwa yimfuyo yabo kanye nabo, ngakube ababoni yini na"
  32,28,Futhi bathi “luyofika nini usuku lokwahlulela uma kungukuthi nina niqinisile na
  32,29,"Ithi, “usuku lokwahlulela angeke lube lusizo kulabo abangakholwa (noma ngabe) bekholwa futhi angeke banikwe ithuba”"
  32,30,Ngakho-ke qhelelana nabo bese uyalinda ngempela bona bangalindileyo
  33,1,"Oh Mphrofethi! Yesaba uMvelinqangi futhi ungabahloniphi abangakholwa kanye nabazenzisi, ngempela uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi uyisazi unobuhlakani"
  33,2,Futhi landela lokho okwembuliwe kuwena okuvela eNkosini yakho ngempela uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi uyakwazi lokho enikwezayo
  33,3,Futhi thembela kuMvelinqangi futhi wanele uMvelinqangi njengomqaphi
  33,4,"UMvelinqangi akekho umuntu amenzela izinhliziyo ezimbili ngaphakathi kuyena futhi akazange enze amakhosikazi enu lawoenenzaisehlukanisonawongokuthinithi(enithi) imihlane yawo injengeyomama benu ukuthi angomama benu futhi akazange enze amadodana enu eniwatholile (lawo angenabo abazali) ukuthi angamadodana enu, lokho yinkulumo yenu eniyisho ngemilomo yenu futhi uMvelinqangi ukhuluma iqiniso futhi yena uholela endleleni (eqondile)"
  33,5,Babizeni ngaboyise lokhu kulungile kakhulu kuMvelinqangi kepha uma ningabazi oyise ngakho-ke bangabafowenu enkolweni nabangane benu futhi alikho icala kunina kulokho enenze kukona iphutha ngaphandle kwalokho izinhliziyo zenu ezikuqondile futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi uyathethelela unesihawu
  33,6,"Umphrofethi usondele kakhulu kwabakholwayo ngaphezu kwabo uqobo. Futhi amakhosikazi akhe angonina (babakholwayo) futhi izihlobo ngobudlelwano zisondelene ezinye zazo kwezinye ngokwesimemezelo sikaMvelinqangi kunabakholwayo nabafuduki ngaphandle kokuba uma nenze okuhle ebanganeni benu, lokhu kubhaliwe encwadini"
  33,7,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi sithatha kubaprofethi isethembiso sabo nakuwena nakuNowa, uAbrahamu, uMose kanye nakuJesu indodana kaMariya futhi sasithatha kubona isethembiso esinqala"
  33,8,Ukuze abuze abaneqiniso ngeqiniso labo futhi wabalungiselela abangakholwayo isijeziso esibuhlungu
  33,9,Oh Nina! EnikholwayokhumbulaniububelebukaMvelinqangi kunina ngenkathi kufika amabutho empi kunina. Ngakho- ke sathumela kuwona umoya namabutho empi eningazange niwabone futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi uyakubona lokho enikwenzayo
  33,10,Khumbula ngenkathi befika kunina beqhamuka ngaphezulu kwenu nangaphansi kwenu nangenkathi kunqundeka amehlo nezinhliziyo zilulekela emiphinjeni futhi nacabanga ngoMvelinqangi imicabango emibi
  33,11,Laphaya balingwa abakholwayo futhi banyakaziswa ukunyakaziswa okunzima
  33,12,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi abazenzisi kanye nalabo ezinhliziyweni zabo okunesifo bethi, ‘’akasethembisanga lutho uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe ngaphandle kwenkohliso.”"
  33,13,"Futhi khumbula nangenkathi iqembu labo lithi, “Oh Bantu baseYathrib! Aninayo indawo yokuma ngakho-ke phindelani emumva” futhi iqembu lacela imvume kumphrofethi lathi, “ngempela izindlu zethu zisobala” futhi (izindlu zabo) zazingavele obala kuphela babefisa ukubaleka"
  33,14,Futhi ukube babengene kubona beqhamuka kuzona zonke izinhlangothi (zedolobha) bese becelwa ukuba bahlasele ngempela babezokwenza lokho futhi babengeke bangabaze ngako ngaphandle nje kokungabaza okuncane
  33,15,Futhi ngempela basenza isethembiso kuMvelinqangi ngaphambilini ukuthi angeke bayiphendule imihlane (yabo) ngasosonke isikhathi isethembiso sikaMvelinqangi siyabuzwa
  33,16,Ithi akusoze kwanisiza ukubaleka uma nibalekela ukufa noma ukubulawa futhi angeke nijatshuliswe ngaphandle kwesikhashana
  33,17,Ithi ngubani lowo onganivikela kuMvelinqangi uma eqonde ukunenza okubi noma eqonde ukuba nomusa kunina na? futhi angeke babatholele umvikeli nomsizi ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi
  33,18,"UMvelinqangi uyabazi phakathi kwenu labo abavimbela abanye kanye nalabo abathi kubafowabo, “wozani kuthina” futhi abayi empini ngaphandle kokuya kancane"
  33,19,"Balusizi kunina kepha uma kufika ukwesaba ubabona bekubukile amehlo abo ephenduka njengalowo owesaba ukufa, kepha uma ukwesaba sekuphelile banintinyela ngezilimi ezihlabayo belangazelela izinto ezinhle labo abakholwa ngakho-ke uMvelinqanga wenza imisebenzi yabo yaba yize leze, futhi ngasosonke isikhathi lokho kulula kuMvelinqangi"
  33,20,"Bacabanga ukuthi izinhlangano zempi azihambanga, futhi uma izinhlangano zempi zingase zibuye bangafisa ukuthi bona babesogwadule kanye nezihlali zasogwadule (ama-Arabhu) bebuza mayelana nezindaba zenu futhi ukube babephakathi kwenu babengeke balwe ngaphandle kokulwa okuncane"
  33,21,Ngempela esithunyweni sikaMvelinqangi ninesibonelo sekhethelo (ekufanele nisilandele) kulowo owethembela kuMvelinqangi nasosukwini lokugcina futhi lowo okhumbula uMvelinqangi kaningi
  33,22,"Futhi kwathi lapho amakholwa ezibona izinhlangano athi, “lokhu yilokhu esathenjiswa kona nguMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe futhi uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe bakhuluma iqiniso, futhi akuzange kubanezelele ngalutho ngaphandle kokukholwa nokuzinikela"
  33,23,"Phakathi kwabakholwayo kunamadoda akuqinisekisayo lokho avumelene noMvelinqangi ngako, ngakho-ke phakathi kwabo kunalowo osifezayo isivumelwano sakhe futhi phakathi kwabo kunalowo olindile futhi abazange baguqule (lutho)"
  33,24,"Ukuze uMvelinqangi abanikeze umvuzo abaneqiniso ngeqiniso labo bese ebajezisa abazenzisi uma ethanda noma abathethelele, ngempela uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi uyathethelela unesihawu"
  33,25,"Futhi labo abangakholwanga uMvelinqangi wabaphindisela emumva entukuthelweni yabo, abazange bakuthole okuhle futhi uMvelinqangi wabanela abakholwayo ekulweni futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi unamandla, uphakeme ngamandla"
  33,26,"Futhi wabehlisela phansi labo ababeseka phakathi kwabantu bencwadi besezinqabeni zabo futhi wafaka uvalo ezinhliziyweni zabo, iqembu nalibulala elinye iqembu nalithumba"
  33,27,"Futhi wanenza izindlalifa zezwe, labo nezindlu zabo nengcebo yabo kanye nomhlaba eningakaze niwunyathele futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi unamndla ngaphezu kwezinto zonke"
  33,28,"Oh Mphrofethi! Ithi emakhosikazini akho,”uma nina nifisa impilo yalomhlaba nobuhle bayo ngako-ke wozani ngizoninika isabelo futhi ngizonikhulula ukunikhulula okuhle.”"
  33,29,Futhi uma nina nifuna uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe nendawo yokuhlala yempilo ezayo ngakho-ke ngempela 2 uMvelinqangi wabalungiselela abenzi bokuhle phakathi kwenu umvuzo omkhulu
  33,30,Oh Makhosikazikamphrofethi! Nomangabengubaniphakathi kwenu owenza isono esicacile uyophindelwa kabili isijeziso futhi ngasosonke isikhathi lokho kulula kuMvelinqangi
  33,31,Futhi noma ngabe ngubani phakathi kwenu nina abesifazane (amakhosikazi kamphrofethi) aqotho kuMvelinqangi nasesithunyweni sakhe futhi lowo owenza izenzo ezilungileyo sizomupha umvuzo wakhe ophindwe kabili futhi owesifazane simlungiselele isabelo esisezingeni eliphezulu
  33,32,"Oh Makhosikazi kamphrofethi! anifani ngisho noyedwa wamanye amakhosikazi uma nimesaba uMvelinqangi ningathambi enkulumweni, hleze lowo okunesifo enhliziyweni yakhe abanethemba kepha khulumani inkulumo ngendlela ehloniphekile"
  33,33,"Futhi hlalani ezindlini zenu, futhi ningazivezi njengokuziveza kwezikhathi zokungazi zasendulo futhi yenzani umthandazo nikhokhe izakaah (ingxenye yemali ekhokhwa kwabampofu) futhi nihloniphe uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe, kuphela uMvelinqangi uthanda ukususa izenzo ezimbi kunina Bantu bomndeni futhi anihlanze ngokuhlanzwa okuphelele"
  33,34,"Futhi khumbulani lokho okufundwa ezindlini zenu okungamavesi kaMvelinqangi nobuhlakani, ngempela uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi umnene uyazi"
  33,35,"Ngempela abesilisa abazinikele ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi nabesifazane abazinikele ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi, nabakholwayo besilisa, nabakholwayo besifazane, nabesilisa abaqotho (kuMvelinqangi) nabesifazane abaqotho(kuMvelinqangi) nabesilisa abaneqinisonabesifazane abaneqiniso, nabesilisa ababekezelayo nabesifazane ababekezelayo, nabesilisa abazithobile nabesifazane abazithobile, nabesilisa abaphanayo nabesifazane abaphanayo, nabesilisa abazilayo nabesifazane abazilayo, nabesifazane abazigcinayo izitho zabo zomzimba zangasese, nabesilisa abamkhumbulayo uMvelinqangi kaningi nabesifazane abamkhumbulayo uMvelinqangi kaningi, uMvelnqangi wabalungiselela intethelelo kanye nomvuzo omkhulu"
  33,36,Futhi akusikona okowesilisa okholwayo nowesifazane okholwayo ukuthi uma uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe benquma udaba babenokukhetha odabeni lwabo futhi noma ngabe ngubani ongamhloniphi uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe ngempela uduke ukuduka okucacile
  33,37,"Futhi (khumbula) ngenkathi uthi kulowo uMvelinqangi ayemethwese umusa nawe wamethwesa umusa, “gcina unkosikazi wakho kuwena futhi yesaba uMvelinqangi futhi ukufihle kuwena lokho uMvelinqangi akuveza obala futhi wesaba abantu, uMvelinqangi ufaneleke kakhulu ukuba umesabe” ngakho-ke kwathi lapho uZaid eseqedile ngaye owesifazane engasamdingi sakushadisa naye owesifazane ukuze kungabikhona ubunzima kwabakholwayo mayelana (nemishado) yamakhosikazi amadoda abo uma engawadingi (amakhosikazi awo) futhi ngasosonke isikhathi umthetho kaMvelinqangi awugcwaliseke"
  33,38,"Abukho ubunzima kumphrofethi kulokho uMvelinqangi amnqumela kona, yindlela kaMvelinqangi kulabo asebadlula ngaphambilini futhi ngasosoke isikhathi impoqo kaMvelinqangi udaba olumisiwe"
  33,39,Labo abadlulisela imiyalezo kaMvelinqangi futhi bamesabe bangesabi ngisho namunye ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi futhi uMvelinqangi wanele ekwahluleleni
  33,40,"UMuhammad akasiyena uyise wamadoda enu, kepha uyisithunywa sikaMvelinqangi nesisicilelo sabaphrofethi futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi uyisazi sazozonke izinto"
  33,41,Oh Nina enikholwayo! khumbulani uMvelinqangi ngenkumbulo eningi
  33,42,Futhi mdumiseni ekuseni nakusihlwa
  33,43,Nguyena owethumela izibusiso kunina kanye nezingelosi zakhe ukuze anikhiphe ebumnyameni anilethe ekukhanyeni futhi ngasosonke isikhathi unesihawu kwabakholwayo
  33,44,Isibingelelo sabo ngosuku abayohlangana ngalo naye kuyoba ukuthi ukuthula futhi ubalungiselele umvuzo osezingeni eliphezulu
  33,45,Oh mphrofethi! ngempela thina sakuthumela njengofakazi nomlethi wezindaba ezimmnandi nomxwayisi
  33,46,Nanjengommemeli kuMvelinqangi ngemvume yakhe nanjengelambu elikhanyayo
  33,47,Futhi tshela abakholwayo izindaba ezimnandi ukuthi okwabo okuvela kuMvelinqangi ngumusa omkhulu
  33,48,Futhi ungabahloniphi abangakholwa kanye nabazenzisi futhi ungabanaki futhi yethembela kuMvelinqangi futhi uMvelinqangi wanele njengomhleli wezindaba
  33,49,Oh Ninaenakholwayo! umanishadanabesifazaneabakholwayo bese nenza isehlukaniso nabo ngaphambi kokuba nibathinte ngakho-ke aninaso isikhathi ekufanele nisibale mayelana nabo abesifazane ngakho-ke banikezeni okubathokozisayo bese niyabakhulula ukubakhulula okuhle
  33,50,"Oh mphrofethi! ngempela thina sawenza avumeleka kuwena amakhosikazi akho lawo owawanika izipho zawo zomshado kanye nalawo asesandleni sakho sokudla kulawo uMvelinqangi akunike wona kanye namadodakazi abafowaboyihlo namadodakazi obabekazi bakho namadodakazi kamalume wakho namadodakazi kadadewabo kamama wakho, lawo afuduka kanye nawe nonkosikazi okholwayo uma owesifazane ezinikela kumphrofethi uma umphrofethi efisa ukushada naye ngokwakho kuphela ngaphandle kwabakholwayo ngempela siyakwazi esibanqumela kona mayelana namakhosikazi abo kanye nalabo abasezandleni zabo zokudla (izigqila) ukuze kungabibikho ubunzima kuwena futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo, onesihawu"
  33,51,"Ungambuyisela eceleni noma ngabe ngubani omthandayo kubona abesifazane futhi ungazithathela wena noma ngabe ngubani omthandayo kanye nalowo omfisayo phakathi kwalabo obabuyisele eceleni ngakho-ke alikho icala kuwena, lokho kungcono kakhulu ukuze baduduzeke futhi bangaphatheki kabi bonke bathokoze ngalokho obanika kona futhi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi lokho okusenhliziyweni zenu futhi uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi uyazi uyabekezela"
  33,52,Akavumelekile kuwena amakhosikazi emva kwalokho noma ukuwashintsha ngamanye amakhosikazi yize noma ngabe bukuheha ubuhle bawo ngaphandle kwalabo abasesandleni sakho sokudla (izigqila) futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi ungumqapheli phezu kwezinto zonke
  33,53,"Oh nina enikholwayo! ningangeni ezindlini zomphrofethi ngaphandle kokuba uma ninikiwe imvume yokuzodla (akungafikwa ngokushesha ukuze) kungalindwa ukulungiswa kwako, kepha uma nimenywa ngakho-ke ngenani, uma senidlile hlakazekani (hambani) futhi ningabi ngabahlalayo abalindainkulumongempelalokhokuyamhluphaumphrofethi unamahloni (ukunitshela ukuthi nihambe) ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi akanawo amahloni ngeqiniso futhi uma nicela okuthize emakhosikazini (kamphrofethi) ngakho-ke waceleni ningemumva kwesahlukaniso lokho kumsulwa kakhulu ezinhliziyweni zenu nasezinhliziyweni zawo (amakhosikazi kamphrofethi) futhi akufanele ukuthi nisihluphe isithunywa sikaMvelinqangi futhi ningashadi namakhosikazi aso emva kwaso nanini ngempela lokho kuMvelinqangi kukhulu"
  33,54,Uma nikuveza obala okuthize noma nikufihla ngakho-ke ngempela uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi uyisazi sazo zonke izinto
  33,55,"Alikho icala kuwona (amakhosikazi kamphrofethi) kobaba bawo nasemadodaneni awo nakubafowabo nasemadodaneni abafowabo nasemadodaneni odadewabo nabesifazane babo nakulabo abasezandleni zawo zokudla (izigqila) futhi yesabani uMvelinqangi makhosikazi kamphrofethi, ngempela uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi ungufakazi phezu kwezinto zonke"
  33,56,"Ngempela uMvelinqangi kanye nezingelosi bathumela izibusiso kumphrofethi, Oh Nina enikholwayo! mceleleni izibusiso (kuMvelinqangi) futhi nimbingelele ngesibingelelo esifanelekileyo"
  33,57,Ngempela labo abahlupha uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe uMvelinqangi ubaqalekisile kulomhlaba nasempilweni ezayo futhi wabalungiselela isijeziso esijabhisayo
  33,58,Futhi labo abahlupha abakholwayo besilisa nabesifazane ngokungafanelekile bathwele icala elinga mahloni nesono esicacile
  33,59,"Oh mphrofethi! yithi emakhosikazini akho nasemadodakazini akho nasemakhosikazini amakholwa mabazemboze ngezembatho zabo (kusukela ekhanda kuya ezinyaweni), lokho kugcono kakhulu ukuze abesifazane (abakholwayo) baziwe bangahlushwa futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi uyathethelela, unesihawu"
  33,60,Uma abazenzisi kanye nalabo ezinhliziyweni zabo ekunesifo nabasakazi bezindaba eziyamanga eMadina bengaphezi sizokwenza ukuthi ubanqobe bese bengabe besaba ngomakhelwane bakho khona (eMadina) ngaphandle kwabambalwa
  33,61,Baqalekisiwe noma ngabe yikuphi lapho befunyanwa khona mababanjwe futhi babulawe ngokubulawa okuphelele
  33,62,Yinqubomgomo kaMvelinqangi kulabo asebadlula ngaphambilini futhi awusoze wayithola inguquko kwinqubomgomo kaMvelinqangi
  33,63,"Abantu bayakubuza mayelana nehora ithi, “ulwazi lwalo lukuMvelinqangi kuphela” futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi ngempela iHora lisondele na"
  33,64,Ngempela uMvelinqangi wabaqalekisa abangakholwa futhi wabalungiselela umlilo ovuthayo
  33,65,"Bayohlala kuwona ingunaphakade, angeke bamthole umvikeli nomelekeleli"
  33,66,"Ngosuku lapho ubuso babo buyobe buguqulwe emlilweni bayothi, “Oh sifisa sengathi samhlonipha uMvelinqangi futhi sasihlonipha isithunywa!”"
  33,67,"Futhi bayothi, “Nkosi yethu ngempela sazihlonipha iziphathimandla zethu kanye nabadala bethu ngakho-ke basidukisa endleleni”"
  33,68,Nkosi yethu banikeze isijeziso esiphindiwe kabili futhi ubaqalekise ngesiqalekiso esikhulu
  33,69,Oh Nina enikholwayo! ningabi njengalabo ababehlupha uMose ngakho-ke wayesemkhipha uMvelinqangi kulokho ababekusho futhi wayehloniphekile kuMvelinqangi
  33,70,Oh Nina enikholwayo! yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi nikhulume inkulumo eqondile
  33,71,Uyonilungiselela imisebenzi yenu futhi anithethelele izono zenu futhi noma ngabe ngubani ohlonipha uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe ngempela uzuze impumelelo enkulu
  33,72,"Ngempela sanikela ukwethembela emazulwini nasemhlabeni nasezintabeni kepha (konke) kwenqaba ukukuthwala futhi kwakwesaba, kepha umuntu wakuthwala ngempela yena (umuntu) ngasosonke isikhathi akanabo ubulungiswa, akanalo ulwazi"
  33,73,"Ukuze uMvelinqangi ajezise abazenzisi besilisa nabesifazane nabakhonza izithombe besilisa nabesifazane futhi uMvelinqangi uyophendukela kwabakholwayo besilisa nabesifazane ngentethelelo futhi uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi uyathethelela, unesihawu"
  34,1,Udumo malube kuMvelinqangi okunguyena okungokwakhe noma ngabe yini esemazulwini nanoma ngabe yini esemhlabeni futhi udumo kuyobe kungolwakhe empilweni ezayo futhi yena ungonobuhlakani ungowaziwayo
  34,2,"Wazi noma ngabe yini engena emhlabathini nanoma ngabe yini ephuma kuwona kanye nanoma ngabe yini eyehlayo ivela ezulwini nanoma ngabe yini engena kulona futhi yena ungonomusa, othethelelayo"
  34,3,"Futhi labo abangakholwangwa bathi, “angeke lifike kuthina ihora” ithi “yebo ngeNkosi yami ngempela liyofika kunina, isazi sokungabonwayo asigejwa ngisho noma ngabe yinto encane kangakanani emazulwini ngisho nasemhlabeni ngisho noma kukuncane kakhuku kunalokho ngisho noma ngabe kukukhulu kakhulu kepha kusencwadini ecacile”"
  34,4,"Ukuze abanike umvuzo labo abakholwayo futhi abenza imisebenzi elungileyo labo-ke, okwabo yintethelelo nesabelo esisezingeni eliphezulu"
  34,5,Futhi labo abazabalazayo ukuphikisana namavesi ethu ukuwadikibalisa labo-ke okwabo yisijeziso esinzima esibuhlungu
  34,6,"Futhi labo ababenikezwe ulwazi bayakubona lokho okwembulwa kuwena okuvela eNkosini yakho ukuthi kona kuyiqiniso futhi kuholela endleleni yophakeme ngamandla, ofanelwe ukudunyiswa"
  34,7,"Futhi labo abangakholwanga bathi, “ngakube singanikhombisa yini indoda ezonitshela ukuthi uma senihlukanisiwe ukuhlukaniswa okuphelele (seningeyilutho) ngempela nina nizoba sendalweni entsha?”"
  34,8,"Ngakube uqambela uMvelinqangi amanga noma unokuhlanya na?, kepha labo abangakholelwa empilweni ezayo basesonweni nasekudukeni okukude le"
  34,9,"Ngakube abakuboni yini lokho okungaphambilini kwabo kanye nalokho okungemumva kwabo okwezulu nomhlaba, uma sithanda singenza ukuthi umhlaba ubagwinye noma sehlisele phezu kwabo izicucu zezulu ngempela kulokho kunophawu kuleyo naleyo nceku eyiphendukele (kuMvelinqangi) ngentethelelo"
  34,10,"Futhi ngempela samnikeza uDavide umusa ovela kithina (sathi), “Oh zintaba! mdumiseni uMvelinqangi kanye naye kanye nezinyoni” futhi samthambisela insimbi"
  34,11,"(Sathi) “Yenza izivatho zensimbi ngokuphelele futhi ulinganise iziyingi zamaketango futhi nenze imisebenzi elungileyo, ngempela mina ngiyakubona loko enikwenzayo”"
  34,12,Futhi sawenza umoya wamthobela uSolomoni ikuseni yawo (yayiwuhambo) olungangenyanga futhi intambama yawo (yayiwuhambo) olungangenyanga futhi sawenza umthombo wethusi ukuthi umgobhozele futhi kwakunamaJinn ayesebenza ngaphambili kwakhe ngemvume yeNkosi yakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani wabo ochezukayo empoqweni yethu siyokwenza ukuthi ezwe isijeziso sokusha
  34,13,"(Abantu) babemenzela loko akufisayo okuyizakhiwo eziphakeme, izithombe, izitsha ezinkulu ezingangamathange amanzi nezimbiza zensimbi zokupheka ezinkulu ezizinzisiwe (ezinganyakazi) “Sebenzani Oh mndeni kaDavide ngokubonga! kepha bambalwa ezincekwini zami ababongayo"
  34,14,"Kepha kwathi lapho sesimnqumela ukufa (uSolomoni) akukho okwabatshela ngokufa kwakhe ngaphandle kwesidalwa (isilwane) somhlaba esadla induku yakhe, ngakho-ke kwathi lapho esewela phansi kwawacacela amaJinn ukuthi ukube ayekwazi okungabonwayo ayengeke ahlale esijezisweni esiyihlazo"
  34,15,"NgempelakwakunophawukuShebaezindawenizabozokuhlala, izivande ezimbili ngakwesokudla nangakwesokunxele yidlani esabelweni seNkosi yenu futhi niyibonge, yizwe elihle neNkosi ethethelelayo"
  34,16,Kepha bafulathela (benqaba) ngakho-ke sathumela kubona izikhukhula (amanzi) aphuma edamini futhi sabashintshela izivande zabo ezimbili zaba yizivande zabo ezimbili ezithela izithelo ezibabayo namatamariski (uhlobo lwesihlahla) kanye nezomlothi ezimbalwa
  34,17,Ngalokho sabanika umvuzo ngenxa yokuthi babengabongi bengakholwa futhi asijezisi ngalendlela ngaphandle kwabangakholwa
  34,18,"Futhi senza phakathi kwabo kanye namadolobha esasiwabusisile ukuthi kube amadolobha abonakalayo kalula futhi sahlukanisa phakathi kwawo uhambo, sathi “hambani phakathi kwawo ebusuku nasemini niphephile”"
  34,19,"Kepha bathi, “Nkosi yethu yenza amabanga amade ohambweni lethu futhi bayona bona imiphefumulo yabo sabe sesibenza ondabuzekwayo futhi sabadabula ukudabulwa okuphelele, ngempela kunezimpawu kulokho kubona bonke ababekezelayo ababongayo"
  34,20,"Futhi u-Iblis (uSathane) wawuqinisekisa ngabo umcabango wakhe, ngakho-ke bamlandela ngaphandle kweqembu labakholwayo"
  34,21,"Futhi (uSathane) akanalo igunya phezu kwabo kepha ukuze sazi ukuthi ngubani okholelwa empilweni ezayo kulowo osekungabazeni ngayo, futhi iNkosi yakho ingumlondolozi wazona zonke izinto"
  34,22,Ithi “bizani labo enanibenza (onkulunkulu) esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi abanalutho ngisho nokuncane kakhulu emazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi abanaso isabelo kukona kokubili futhi akanaye umlekeleli phakathi kwabo”
  34,23,"Futhi ukuncengela akusizi kuyena ngaphandle kwalowo amvumelayo kuze kuthi uma ukwesaba kususiwe ezihliziyweni zabo bathi, “yathini iNkosi yenu bathi iqiniso futhi yona iphakeme yinkulu”"
  34,24,"Ithi, “ngubani oninika isabelo esivela emazulwini nasemhlabeni na?” ithi, “nguMvelinqangi” futhi ngempela yithina noma yinina mhlawumbe abasekuholweni noma abasekudukeni okucacile"
  34,25,Ithi angeke nibuzwe ngecala lethu futhi angeke sibuzwe ngalokho enikwenzayo
  34,26,"Ithi, iNkosi yethu iyosiqoqela ndawomye bese iyehlulela phakathi kwethu ngeqiniso futhi yona ingumehluleli onolwazi"
  34,27,"Ithi ngikhombiseni labo enanimenzela abahlanganyeli ngabo, lutho! kepha yena unguMvelinqangi uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani"
  34,28,"Futhi asizange sikuthumele ngaphandle kokuba ngumlethi wezindaba ezimnandi nomxwayisi kubantu bonke, kepha iningi labantu alazi"
  34,29,Futhi bathi siyofika nini lesisithembiso uma kungukuthi nina niqinisile na
  34,30,Ithi isinqumo senu esosuku eningeke nikwazi ukulihlehlisa ihora futhi eningeke nikwazi ukulisheshisa
  34,31,"Futhi labo abangakholwanga bathi, “asisoze sikholelwe kuleQur’an ngisho noma kulokho okungaphambilini kwayo”, futhi uma ungazibona izoni zimisiwe ngaphambili kweNkosi yazo, ezinye zazo ziphendukela kwezinye ngezwi (lokusola), labo ababenziwe buthakathaka bayothi kulabo ababeqhosha “ukube kwakungesingenxa yenu sasizoba ngabakholwayo”"
  34,32,Labo ababeqhosha bathi kulabo ababenziwe buthakathaka “ngakube yithina yini esanivimbela ekuholweni emva kokuba sekunifikele na? Qhabo nina naniyizoni”
  34,33,"Futhi labo ababenziwe buthakathaka bathi kulabo ababeqhosha “kepha kwakuyisu lenu lasebusuku nasemini ngenkathi nisiphoqa ukuthi singakholwa kuMvelinqangi nokuthi simbekele izimbangi” futhi bayokufihla ukuzisola uma sebesibona isijeziso futhi siyowagaxa amaketango ezintamweni zalabo abangakholwanga, ngakube bayonikwa umvuzo ngaphandle kwalokho ababekwenza na"
  34,34,"Futhi sasingakaze simthumele umxwayisi edolobheni ngaphandle kokuthi abanothile balo bathi, “ngempela asikholelwa kulokho enithunywe ngako”"
  34,35,"Futhi bathi, “thina sinengcebo eningi kakhulu kanye nezingane futhi thina angeke sijeziswe"
  34,36,Ithi ngempela iNkosi yami iyasandisa isabelo kulowo emthandayo futhi isinciphiso kepha iningi labantu alazi
  34,37,Futhi akusiyona ingcebo yenu noma izingane zenu ezinisondeza eduzane nathi kepha yilabo abakholwayo futhi abenza imisebenzi emihle elungileyo labo-ke okwabo umvuzo ophindiwe kabili ngenxa yalokho ababekwenza futhi bayohlala ezindaweni zokuhlala bephephile
  34,38,Futhi labo abazabalazayo ukuphikisana namavesi ethu ukuwadikibalisa labo-ke bayolethwa esijezisweni
  34,39,Ithi ngempela iNkosi yami iyaselula isabelo kunoma ngabe ngubani eyimthandayo ezincekwini zayo futhi imnciphisele futhi noma ngabe yini oluthize enilusebenzisayo (eninikela ngalo) ngakho-ke yona iyolubuyisa futhi yona ingcono kunabobonke abanika isabelo”
  34,40,"Futhi ngosuku eyobaqoqela ngalo ndawonye bonke bese ithi ezingelosini, “ngakube yibona yini laba ababenikhonza na?”"
  34,41,"(Izingelosi) ziyothi, “udumo malube kuwe! wena ungumvikeli wethu hhayi bona, kepha babekhonza amaJinn, abaningi babo babengabakholelwa kuwona”"
  34,42,"Ngakho-ke ngalolusuku abekho abanye benu abaphathela abanye inzuzo nokulimala futhi siyothi kulabo abona, “yizwani isijeziso somlilo leso enanisiphika”"
  34,43,"Futhi uma befundelwa amavesi ethu acacile bathi, “lona akayilutho ngaphandle kokuba yindoda eyithanda ukunivimbela kulokho okwakukhonzwa ngoyihlo”, futhi bathi “lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle kwamanga aqanjiwe futhi bathi labo abazange bakholwe mayelana neqiniso ngenkathi lifika kubona “lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle komlingo ocacile”"
  34,44,Futhi asibanikezanga izincwadi ababengazifunda futhi asizange simthumele kubona umxwayisi ngaphambilini kwakho
  34,45,Nalabo ababengaphambilini kwabo baliphika (iqiniso) futhi laba abakayitholi ngisho ingxenye eyodwa eshumini yaloko esabanika kona (abasendulo) kepha baziphika izithunywa zami ngakho-ke kwakunjani ukuphika kwami
  34,46,"Ithi kuphela nginelulekela entweni eyodwa ukuthi niphakamele uMvelinqangi ngababili nangamunye bese niyacabanga ukuthi benikanye naye akukho ukuhlanya kuye, akayilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngumxwayisi wenu ngaphambi kwesijeziso esinzima"
  34,47,"Ithi noma ngabe yimuphi umvuzo, engiwucela kunina ungowenu, umvuzo wami ukuMvelinqangi kuphela futhi yena ungufakazi phezu kwezinto zonke"
  34,48,"Ithi ngempela iNkosi yami iyaliveza iqiniso, isazi sokungabonwayo"
  34,49,Ithi iqiniso selifikile futhi inkohliso angeke isungulwe futhi angeke iphindwe
  34,50,Ithiumangiphambukakuphelangiphambukelaumphefumulo wami futhi uma ngiholiwe kungenxa yalokho iNkosi yami ekwembulile kumina ngempela yona iyezwa isondele
  34,51,"Futhi uma ungababona lapho sebesaba, ngakho-ke angeke baphunyuke futhi bayobanjwa endaweni eseduzane"
  34,52,"Futhi bayothi, “siyakholelwa kuyona” kepha bangakuthola kanjani lokho (iqiniso) besendaweni ekude na"
  34,53,Futhi ngempela abakholelwanga kulona (iqiniso) ngaphambilini futhi babengathekisa ngokungabonwayo basendaweni ekude
  34,54,"Futhi kuyobekwa okuhlukanisayo phakathi kwabo naloko abakufisayo njengoba kwenziwa kwabafananabo ngaphambilini, ngempela bona basekungabazeni okukhulu"
  35,1,"Udumo lungolukaMvelinqangi umsunguli wamazulu nomhlaba owenza izingelosi izithunywa ezinamaphiko angambili nangantathu nangane uyakwandisa endalweni lokho akuthandayo, ngempela uMvelinqangi unamandla okwenza zonke izinto"
  35,2,"Noma ngabe yini uMvelinqangi ayinikeza abantu emseni ngakho-ke akekho ongayigodla, futhi noma ngabe yini ayigodlayo akekho ongayikhulula ngemva kwakhe futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani"
  35,3,"Oh Bantu! khumbulani ububele bukaMvelinqangi kunina, ngakube ukhona yini omunye umdali ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangioninikaisabeloesivelaezulwininasemhlabeni na? Akekho onelungelo lokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe, nimfulathelelani na"
  35,4,Futhi uma bekuphika ngempela zaziphikwa izithunywa ngaphambilini kwakho futhi ikuMvelinqangi lapho zibuyiselwa khona izindaba
  35,5,Oh Bantu! ngempela isethembiso sikaMvelinqangi siyiqiniso ngakho-ke ayinganikhohlisi impilo yalomhlaba futhi akanganikhohlisi umkhohlisi ngoMvelinqangi
  35,6,"Ngempela usathane uyisitha senu, ngakho-ke mthatheni njengesitha kuphela umema iqembu lakhe ukuze libengabanye babangane bomlilo"
  35,7,Labo abangakholwanga okwabo yisijeziso esinzima. Futhi okwalaboabakholwayofuthiabenzaizenzoezinhleezilungileyo yintethelelo kanye nomvuzo omkhulu
  35,8,"Ngakube lowo owenzelwe izenzo zakhe ezimbi zabukeka zizinhle uzibona zizinhle ngakho-ke ngempela uMvelinqangi udukisa lowo amthandayo, futhi uholela (endleleni eqondile) lowo amthandayo, ngakho-ke awungaphatheki kabi umphefumulo wakho ngabo, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyisazi ngalokho abakwenzayo"
  35,9,"Futhi nguMvelinqangi othumela imimoya bese iphakamisa amafu bese siwathumela ezweni elifile sivuse ngawo umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo, kunjalo ukuvuswa kokufileyo"
  35,10,"Noma ngabe ngubani ofisa ukuhlonipheka ngakho-ke ukuhlonipheka konke kungokukaMvelinqangi, kuyena kukhuphukelaizwielihlekanyenomsebenziomuhleolungileyo uyalenyusa futhi labo abenza amacebo ngezinto ezimbi okwabo yisijeziso esinzima futhi icebo labo liyashabalala"
  35,11,"Futhi uMvelinqangi wanidala ngothuli kwasekuba ingeconsi lesidoda wayesenenza nabangambili, futhi akekho owesifazane okhulelwe otetayo ngaphandle kolwazi lwakhe futhi akusikona ukuthi umuntu omdala welulelwa iminyaka noma incishiswe iminyaka yakhe kepha kusencwadini ngempela lokho kulula kuMvelinqangi"
  35,12,"Futhi ulwandle olubili alufani lolu luhlwabusile lusashukela luyaphuzeka, loluya lusasawoti luyababa, kulona (lolubili) nidla inyama emnandi (izinhlanzi) futhi nikhipha imihlobiso eniyigqokayo futhi ubona imikhumbi ihamba kulona (ulwandle) ukuze nifune umusa wakhe futhi ukuze mhlawumbe nibonge"
  35,13,"Wenza ukuthi ubusuku bungenele emini futhi wenza ukuthi imini ingenele ebusukwini futhi wenza ukuthi ilanga nenyanga ngakunye kuhambe isikhathi esinqunyiwe, lowo nguMvelinqangi iNkosi yenu, ubukhosi bungobakhe futhi labo enibamemezayo esikhundleni sakhe abanawo ngisho umucwana wohlamvu lwesundu"
  35,14,Uma nibamemeza abawuzwa umthandazo wenu futhi noma ngabe bayezwa abakwazi ukuniphendula futhi ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo bayophika ukuzibandakanya kanye nani futhi akekho ongakutshela (lokhu) onjengonolwazi
  35,15,Oh Bantu! Nina ningabadinga uMvelinqangi kepha yena uMvelinqangi akadingi lutho ungodunyiswayo
  35,16,Uma ethanda anganisusa bese enza indalo entsha
  35,17,Futhi lokho kuMvelinqangi akunzima
  35,18,"Futhi akekho umthwali wemithwalo oyothwala umthwalo womunye futhi uma omunye ethwele okusindayo ubiza omunye ukuthwala umthwalo wakhe, akekho oyothwala ingxenye kuwona ngisho noma ngabe yisihlobo esisondele, kuphela ungabaxwayisa labo abesaba iNkosi yabo engabonwayo futhi abenza umthandazo futhi noma ngabe ngubani ozihlanzayo kuphela uzihlanzela umphefumulo wakhe futhi sikuMvelinqangi isiphetho"
  35,19,Futhi akefani ongaboni nobonayo
  35,20,Ngisho nobumnyama nokukhanya (akufani)
  35,21,Ngisho nomthunzi nokushisa kwelanga (akufani)
  35,22,"Futhi abefani abaphilayo nabafileyo, ngempela uMvelinqangi wenza ukuthi ezwe lowo amthandayo futhi wena awusiyena owenza ukuthi bezwe labo abasemangcwabeni"
  35,23,Wena awuyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngumxwayisi
  35,24,"Ngempela sakuthumela neqiniso njengomlethi wezindaba ezimnandi nomxwayisi, futhi asikho isizwe ekungazange kudlule kusona umxwayisi"
  35,25,"Futhi uma bekuphika ngempela labo ababengaphambilini kwabo baphikwa, zafika kubona izithunywa zabo nezimpawu ezicacile nemibhalo kanye nencwadi ekhanyisayo"
  35,26,Ngabe sengiyababamba labo ababengakholwa (bheka) ukuthi kwakunjani ukubaphika kwami
  35,27,Awuboni yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi wehlisela phansi amanzi avela esibhakabhakeni esiveza ngawo izithelo ezinemibala eyizinhlobonhlobo futhi ezintabeni kunezindlela ezimhlophe nezibomvu ezemibala eyehlukehlukene (ezinye) zimnyama kakhulu
  35,28,"Futhi phakathi kwabantu nasezilwaneni kanye nasezinkomeni kunemibala eyehlukehlukene, kuphela abesaba uMvelinqangi ezincekwini zakhe abanolwazi, ngempela uMvelinqangi uphakeme ngamandla ungothethelelayo"
  35,29,Ngempela labo abayifundayo incwadi kaMvelinqangi benze umthandazo futhi basebenzise (banikele) kulokho esababela kukona esithe nasobala bethembele ohwebweni olungasoze lwashabalala
  35,30,"Ukuze abakhokhele imivuzo yabo ngokugcwele futhi abanezelele emseni wakhe, ngempela yena uyathethelela uyabonga"
  35,31,"Futhi loko esikwambulile kuwena kwencwadi kuyiqiniso eligcwalisela lokho okungaphambilini kwayo, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyazi uyazibona izinceku zakhe"
  35,32,"Sabe sesibanikeza incwadi njengendlalifa labo esabakhethayo ezincekwini zethu, ngakho-ke phakathi kwabo kunalowo owona umphefumulo wakhe futhi phakathi kwabo kunalowo omaphakathi nendawo futhi phakathi kwabo kunalowo ophambili kunabo bonke ezenzweni ezinhle ngemvume kaMvelinqangi lokho kungumusa omkhulu"
  35,33,"Izivande zangunaphakade abayongena kuzona, lapho phakathi bayohlotshiswa ngezigqizo zegolide nangobuhlalo futhi izingubo zabo lapho phakathi kuyoba ngezikasilika"
  35,34,"Futhi bayothi, “udumo malube kuMvelinqangi okunguyena owasusa usizi kuthina! ngempela iNkosi yethu iyathethelela iyabonga”"
  35,35,"(Inkosi) esihlalise endaweni yokuhlala yangunaphakade, ngomusa wayo futhi lapho phakathi angeke kusithinte ukusebenza futhi lapho phakathi angeke kusithinte ukukhathala"
  35,36,"Futhi labo abangakholwanga okwabo ngumlilo wesihogo, asikho isikhathi esinqunyiwe kubona ukuthi bafe futhi angeke bancishiselwe esijezisweni sawo, sibanika umvuzo kanjalo bonke abangabongi"
  35,37,"Futhi lapho phakathi bayokhalela (usizo) “Nkosi yethu sikhiphe sizokwenza izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo hhayi lezo esasizenza” asizange yini sininike impilo ende ngokwanele ukuze noma ngabe ngubani owayengayaleka ayaleke na? Futhi wafika kunina umxwayisi, ngakho-ke yizwani abayizoni angeke babenaye umsizi"
  35,38,Ngempela uMvelinqangi uyisazi sokungabonwayo samazulu nomhlaba ngempela yena uyakwazi lokho okusezifubeni
  35,39,Nguyena owanenza ukuba ngabalandelayo ngokuhlala emhlabeni. Ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani ongakholwa kukuyena ukungakholwa kwakhe futhi akubanezezeli abangakholwa ukungakholwa kwabo eNkosini yabo ngaphandle kokunengeka futhi akubanezeleli (ngalutho) abangakholwa ukungakholwa kwabo ngaphandle kokulahlekelwa
  35,40,"Ithi, “ngakube nibabonile yini abahlanganyeli benu labo enibabizayo esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi na?, Ngikhombiseni ukuthi yini abayidalayo emhlabeni noma ngakube banomhlanganyeli emazulwini na? Noma ngakube sabanikeza incwadi bona basebufakazini obucacile kuyona na? Qhabo! izoni azithembisani lutho ngaphandle kwenkohliso”"
  35,41,Ngempela uMvelinqangi uyawabamba amazulu nomhlaba ukuthi angasuki endaweni yawo futhi uma esuka endaweni yawo akekho ngisho noyedwa ongawabamba womabili emva kwakhe ngempela yena ngasosonke isikhathi uyabekezela uyathethelela
  35,42,Futhi bafunga ngoMvelinqangi izifungo zabo ezinqala ukuthi uma kungase kufike umxwayisi kubona bangaba ngabaholwe kakhulu ngaphezu kwanoma yiziphi izizwe kepha kwathi lapho sekufika umxwayisi kubona abazange banezelelwe yilutho ngaphandle kokukugwema lokho
  35,43,Beqhosha emhlabeni futhi benza icebo elibi futhi icebo elibi alimsingathi omunye umuntu ngaphandle kwabantu balo ngakho-ke ngakube kukhona yini abakulindele ngaphandle kwendlela yasemandulo na? Kepha awusoze uyifumane inguquko endleleni kaMvelinqangi futhi awusoze ukufumane ukuchezuka endleleni kaMvelinqangi
  35,44,Abazange yini bahambe ezweni babone ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho salabo ababengaphambilini kwabo futhi babeqatha ngamandla kunabo futhi uMvelinqangi akukho lutho elimphunyukayo emazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi yena ngasosonke isikhathi uyazi unamandla okwenza
  35,45,Futhi ukube uMvelinqangi wayengase abajezise abantu ngenxa yalokho abakusebenzele wayengeke azishiye izidalwa ezinyakazayo (izilwane) phezu kwawo (umhlaba) kepha ubayekela isikhathi esinqunyiwe ngakho-ke uma kufika isikhathi sabo ngempela uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi ungumboni wezinceku zakhe
  36,1,Ya’ seen
  36,2,NgeQur’an enobuhlakani
  36,3,Ngempela wena ungomunye wezithunywa
  36,4,Endleleni eqondile
  36,5,Isambulo sophakeme ngamandla onesihawu
  36,6,Ukuze wexwayise abantu ababengaxwayiswanga oyise ngakho- ke bona abanakile
  36,7,Ngempela izwi laqiniseka kwabaningi babo kepha bona bakholwa
  36,8,Ngempela thina sibeke amaketango ezintanyeni zabo afinyelela ezilevini ukuze amakhanda abo abheke phezulu
  36,9,Futhi sibeke okuvimbelayo ngaphambi kwabo nokumvimbelayo ngemva kwabo sabe sesiyabamboza ukuze bangaboni
  36,10,"Futhi\tkuyefana\tkubona\tnoma\tuyabaxwayisa\tnoma awubaxwayisi angeke bakholwe"
  36,11,"Kuphela ungakwazi ukuxwayisa lowo olandela isikhumbuzo futhi owesaba onomusa ongabonwayo, ngakho-ke mnike izindaba ezimnandi ngentethelelo nangomvuzo osezingeni eliphezulu"
  36,12,"Ngempela\tthina\tsiyabaphilisa\tabafile\rfuthi\rsikubhala phansi lokho abakubeke ngaphambili\rkanye\r(nalokho) okusezinyathelweni\tzabo\tfuthi\tzonke\rizinto\rsizibhalile emholini ocacile"
  36,13,Futhi benzele isibonelo sabantu bedolobha ngenkathi kufika kulona izithunywa
  36,14,Ngenkathi sithumela kubona (izithunywa) ezimbili base beyaziphika zombili sabe sesiyabaqinisa ngowesithathu basebethi “ngempela thina sithunyiwe kunina
  36,15,Bathi (abantu bedolobha) “nina aniyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngabantu abafana nathi futhi onomusa akazange ambule lutho kuphela nina niqamba amanga”
  36,16,Zathi (izithunywa) “Inkosi yethu iyazi ukuthi thina siyizithunywa kunina”
  36,17,Futhi alikho icala kuthina ngaphandle kokudlulisela umyalezo ocacile
  36,18,"Bathi, “ngempela thina sibona ukubikezela okubi kunina uma ningaphezi ngempela sizonikhanda ngamatshe futhi nizothintwa yisijeziso esibuhlungu esivela kuthina”"
  36,19,"Zathi (izithunywa), “ukubikezela kwenu kukanye nani ngoba nikhunjuzisiwe kepha nina ningabantu abephula umthetho”"
  36,20,Futhi kwafika indoda ivela engxenyeni ebuqamama yedolobha igijima yathi “Oh Bantu bami! landelani izithunywa”
  36,21,Landelani labo abangawuceli umvuzo kunina futhi bona bangabaholelwe endleleni elungileyo
  36,22,Futhi kungani ukuthi ngingamkhonzi lowo owangidalayo futhi niyobubuyiselwa kuyena
  36,23,"Ngakube ngingazithathela omunye uNkulunkulu wamanga esikhundleni sakhe kulapho onomusa ehlose inhlupheko kumina na?, angeke kungisize ngalutho ukungincengela kwabo futhi angeke bangisindise"
  36,24,Ngempela mina ngiyobe ngisekudukeni okucacile
  36,25,Ngempela mina ngikholiwe eNkosini yenu ngakho-ke ngilaleleni
  36,26,"Kwathiwa, “ngena esivandeni (ezulwini)” wathi, “ngifisa sengathi abantu bami bangazi”"
  36,27,Ngokuthi iNkosi yami ingithethelele futhi yangibeka kanye nabahloniphekileyo
  36,28,Futhi asiyehliselanga phezulu kwabantu bakhe emva kwakhe impi evela ezulwini futhi kwakungadingeki ukuthi siyithumele
  36,29,Kwakungeyilutho kepha kwakungumsindo owodwa masinyane babethule du
  36,30,Oh ukuzisola ebantwini! Kwakungakaze kufike kubona isithunywa ngaphandle kokuthi babesenza inhlekisa
  36,31,Ngakube ababoni yini ukuthi zingaki izizukulwane esazibhubhisa ngaphambilini kwabo zona angeke zibuyele kubona
  36,32,Futhi ngempela bonke-bonke bayolethwa ngaphambili kwethu
  36,33,Futhi uphawu lwabo umhlaba ofile sawuphilisa sabe sesiveza kuwona uhlamvu kuze badle kulona
  36,34,Futhi kuwona sazenza izivande zamasundu nezamagilebhisi futhi kuwona sayenza imithombo ukuthi iqhume
  36,35,Ukuze badle ezithelweni zawo futhi izandla zabo azizitshalanga (izithelo) ngakube ababongi yini na
  36,36,Udumo malube kulowo owadala kwaba ngakubili kukona konke okuvezwa umhlaba kanye nokohlobo lwabo nakulokho abangakwazi
  36,37,"Futhi uphawu lwabo ubusuku, siyalukhipha usuku kubona kulapho bona besebumnyameni"
  36,38,"Futhi ilanga lihamba njalo liya lapho liphelela khona, lokho kungempoqo yophakeme ngamandla oyisazi"
  36,39,Nenyanga siyinqumele izimo ezibonakalayo kuze kube yilapho iphenduka iba njengegatsha lesundu elidala elomile
  36,40,Akusikhona okwelanga ukuthi lifice inyanga noma ubusuku ukuthi budlule imini futhi konke kuhamba emkhondweni
  36,41,Futhi uphawu lwabo ukuthi sayithwala inzalo yabo emkhunjini othweleyo
  36,42,"Futhi sibadalele okufana nako, lokhu abakugibelayo"
  36,43,Futhi uma sithanda singabaminzisa ngakho-ke angeke balekelelwe futhi bona angeke bahlengwe
  36,44,Ngaphandle komusa ovela kuthina kanye nenjabulo yesikhashana
  36,45,Futhi uma kuthiwa kubona “qaphelani loko okungaphambili kwenu kanye nalokho okungemumva kwenu ukuze mhlawumbe nithole umusa”
  36,46,Futhi alifiki kubona ivesi emavesini eNkosi yabo ngaphandle kokuba bayalifulathela
  36,47,Futhi uma kuthiwa kubona “sebenzisani kulokho anabela kona uMveliqangi” labo abangakholwanga bathi kulabo abakholwayo “ngakube singodla lowo okungathi uma ethanda uMvelinqangi amondle?” Anikwiyilutho ngaphandle kokuba sephutheni eligqamile
  36,48,"Futhi bathi, “siyofika nini lesisithembiso uma kungukuthi nina niqinisile?”"
  36,49,Abalindele lutho ngaphandle kokukhala okukodwa okuyobathatha kulapho bona bephikisana
  36,50,Ngakho-ke angeke bakwazi ukwenza ifa noma ukubuyela ebantwini babo
  36,51,Futhi liyoshawa icilongo kulapho bona beyophuma emathuneni beshesha bebheke eNkosini yabo
  36,52,"Bayothi, “Oh usizi kuthina! Ngubani lowo osivuse endaweni yethu, lokhu kuyilokhu onomusa akwethembisa nezithunywa zakhuluma iqiniso”"
  36,53,Angeke kube yilutho ngaphandle kokukhala okukodwa kulapho bona bonke beyolethwa ngaphambili kwethu
  36,54,Ngakho-ke ngalolusuku umphefumulo angeke wenziwe okungenabo ubulungiswa ngalutho futhi angeke ninikwe umvuzo ngaphandle kwaloko enanikwenza
  36,55,Ngempela izihlali zesivande kulolosuku ziyobamatasatasa ngezinto eziyinjabulo
  36,56,"Bona kanye namakhosikazi abo bayoba semthunzini, bacambalale endaweni ephakeme"
  36,57,Okwabo lapho phakathi yizithelo futhi okwabo kuyoba yinoma ngabe yini abayicelayo
  36,58,Ukuthula! Izwi elivela eNkosini enesihawu
  36,59,Futhi hlukanani namuhla Oh nina eniyizoni
  36,60,Angizange yini nginiphoqe Oh bantwana ba-Adam! Ukuthi ningamkhonzi usathane? Ngempela yena uyisitha senu esigqamile
  36,61,Nokuthi nikhonze mina? Lena yindlela elungile
  36,62,Futhi ngempela wadukisa iqembu elikhulu phakathi kwenu ngakube naningenawo yini umqondo
  36,63,Lesi yisihogo enanethenjiswe sona
  36,64,Ngenani kusona namhlanje ngenxa yokuthi naningakholwa
  36,65,Kulolusuku siyayisicilela imilomo yabo futhi izandla zabo zizokhuluma nezinyawo zabo zizofakaza mayelana naloko ababekusebenzela
  36,66,Futhi ukube besithanda besizosusa amehlo abo bese beyaphuphutheka endleleni bese bebona kanjani
  36,67,Futhi ukube besithanda besizobaguqula ezindaweni zabo bebengeke besakwazi ukuya phambili nokuphindela emumva
  36,68,"Futhi noma ngabe ngubani esimnika impilo ende simhlehlisela emumva endalweni, ngakube abanawo yini umqondo na"
  36,69,"Futhi asimfundisanga ubumbongi futhi akumfanele, yona ayiyilutho ngaphandle kwesikhumbuzo neQur’an ecacile"
  36,70,Ukuze ixwayise noma ngabe ngubani ophilayo futhi kuqiniseke izwi ukubhekana nabangakholwa
  36,71,Ababoni yini ukuthi sabadalela kuloko okwenziwe yizandla zethu izinkomo abangabanini bazo na
  36,72,Futhi sabathobisela zona ngakho-ke ezinye phakathi kwazo bayazigibela futhi ezinye phakathi kwazo bayazidla
  36,73,"Futhi banenzuzo kuzona kanye neziphuzo, ngakube ababongi yini na"
  36,74,Futhi esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi bazithathela izithixo ukuze mhlawumbe bathole usizo
  36,75,Azikwazi ukubasiza futhi bona kuzona bayibutho elilethwe ngaphambili
  36,76,Ngakho-ke ayingakuphathi kabi inkulumo yabo ngempela thina siyakwazi lokho abakufihlayo kanye nalokho abakuveza obala
  36,77,Ngakube umuntu akaboni yini ukuthi samdala ngeconsi lesidoda kulapho yena eyisitha esigqamile
  36,78,"Futhi wasenzela isibonelo wakhohlwa yindalo yakhe wathi, “ngubani onika amathambo impilo uma esewuthuli na?”"
  36,79,"Ithi, “uwanika impilo lowo owadalayo ngesikhathi sokuqala futhi yena uyisazi sazona zonke izidalwa”"
  36,80,Lowo owanibekela umlilo esihlahleni esiluhlaza kulapho nina nokhela kuwona
  36,81,Angeke yini lowo owadala amazulu nomhlaba akwazi ukudala okufana nabo na? Yebo! Yena ungumdali owaziyo
  36,82,"Kuphela, impoqo yakhe, uma ehlose into ethize uthi kuyona “yenzeka” bese iyenzeka"
  36,83,Ngakho-ke udumo malube kulowo esandleni sakhe ekunombuso wezinto zonke futhi niyophindiselwa kuyena